\id JDG
\h Řquḍat
\toc1 Řquḍat
\toc2 Řquḍat
\toc3 Řqḍ.
\mt1 Řquḍat
\c 1
\s1 Yahuda idweř d azeǧif awarni i řmewt n Yacuwa
\m 
\v 1 Awarni i řmewt n Yacuwa, imsar aqa ayt n Israil sseqsan SIDI, nnan: “Man wen zzayneɣ i ɣa ikkaren d amezwaru ad igeɛɛed ad immneɣ ak-d ayt n Kenɛan?” \x ◘ \xo 1:1 \xt Řqḍ. 20:18\x*
\v 2 Yarra-dd SIDI: “Yahuda ad igeɛɛed \add d amezwaru\add*. Xzar, Necc wciɣ as tammurt deg ufus nnes.”
\v 3 Uca inna Yahuda i umas Cimɛun: “Geɛɛed akidi di \add temmurt n\add* tqedduḥt \add n řeɛbar\add* inu uca ejj aneɣ ad nemmneɣ ak-d ayt n Kenɛan, \add xenni\add* necc ad kik geɛɛdeɣ di \add temmurt n\add* tqedduḥt nnec.” Uca yuyur akides Cimɛun.
\m 
\v 4 Igeɛɛed Yahuda uca SIDI iɛarn ayt n Kenɛan d Ifiriziy\add yen\add* deg ufus nsen uca ɣeřben xasen ɣar Bazaq, ɛecra-ařaf n yiryazen. \f ◼ \fr 1:4 \fk Bazaq\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘assam’.\f*
\v 5 Nitni ufin Aduni-Bazaq di Bazaq uca mmenɣen akides u nitni ɣeřben x ayt n Kenɛan u x Ifiriziy\add yen\add*.
\v 6 \add Maca\add* Aduni-Bazaq yarweř uca nitni ḍfaren t uca ṭṭfen t uca qessen as imzawen \add d tfednin timeqqranin\add* zeg ifassen nnes u zeg iḍaren nnes.
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* inna Aduni-Bazaq: “Sebɛin n ijeǧiden, ttwaqessen asen imzawen \add d tfednin\add*, tuɣa řeqqḍen \add iřeqqʷaz\add* sadu ṭṭabřa inu. Mammec i kidsen ggiɣ, ammu i d ayi ixeǧeṣ AREBBI!” Iwyen t ɣar Urcalim uca netta immut dinni.
\m 
\v 8 Ayt n Yahuda mmenɣen ak-d Urcalim uca ṭṭfen tt, wtin tt s řeqḍeɛ n ssif uca qqeden tandint s tmessi.
\m 
\v 9 Awarni as hwan ayt n Yahuda ḥima ad mmenɣen ak-d ayt n Kenɛan, inni izeddɣen di Temmurt n Idurar, di \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub u di Temmurt Iwaṭan. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Yac. 10:36; 11:21; 15:13\x*
\m 
\v 10 Iffeɣ Yahuda ɣar ayt n Kenɛan i tuɣa izeddɣen di Ḥabrun. Isem n Ḥabrun \add tuɣa\add* zic qqaren as Qaryat-Arbaɛ. Nitni ɣeřben x Cicay d Aximan d Talmay. \x ◘ \xo 1:10 \xt Yac. 15:14\x*
\v 11 Ssenni iffeɣ ɣar imezdaɣ n Dabir. Isem n Dabir \add tuɣa\add* zic qqaren as Qaryat-Safar. \x ◘ \xo 1:11 \xt Yac. 15:15-19.\x*
\v 12 Inna Kalib: “Wenni i ɣa iwten Qaryat-Safar ad tt iṭṭef, ad as wceɣ yeǧi Axsa d tamɣart.”
\v 13 Ɛutniyil, mmis n Qinaz, umas ameẓyan n Kalib, iṭṭef i-tt. Uca Kalib iwca as yeǧis Axsa d tamɣart. \f ◼ \fr 1:13 \fk Ɛutniyil\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘ayrad n Arebbi’.\f*
\v 14 Imsar umi \add ɣares\add* dd-tusa nettat, tɛarn i-t s tutra x yeyyar n babas. Uca teḍra x weɣyuř. Isseqsa tt Kalib: “Min cem yuɣin?” \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Yac. 15:18\x*
\v 15 Nettat tarra-dd xas: “Ewc ayi ict n lbaraka, minzi tewcid ayi ict n treqqiɛt n temmurt \add ɣar\add* ljanub. Ttzawgeɣ, ewc ayi uřa d řɛunṣarat!” Uca iwca as Kalib řɛunṣarat n nej d řɛunṣarat n wadday.
\m 
\v 16 Geɛɛden arraw n Uqini, wenni d aḍegʷař n Musa, ak-d ayt n Yahuda zi Tendint n Tcejjura n Tini ɣar řexřa n Yahuda nni \add iǧan\add* di \add Temmurt n\add* Ljanub ɣar Ɛarad. Ffɣen nitni, zeddɣen ak-d řgens. \f ◼ \fr 1:16 \fk Tandint n Tcejjura n Tini\ft - aqa-tt d tandint n Ariḥa.\f*
\v 17 Iruḥ Yahuda ak-d umas Cimɛun uca ɣeřben nitni x ayt n Kenɛan inni i tuɣa izeddɣen di Ṣafat, ḥarrmen ten qaɛ uca teḥḥan ten uca ggin as i tendint \add nni\add* Ḥurma.
\v 18 Iṭṭef Yahuda uřa d Ɣazza ak-d temmurt nnes d Acqalun ak-d temmurt nnes d Ɛaqrun ak-d temmurt nnes.
\v 19 SIDI tuɣa-t ak-d Yahuda ařami yuẓẓeř x \add imezdaɣ n\add* Temmurt n Idurar, maca \add imezdaɣ\add* n řewda n teɣzurt war izemmar ad xasen yaẓẓeř \add zi tesɣart nsen\add*, minzi nitni tuɣa ɣarsen ikarruten n umenɣi n wuzzař.
\v 20 I Kalib wcin as Ḥabrun, am mammec tuɣa inna Musa, uca netta yuẓẓeř ssenni x třata n iḥenjiren n Ɛanaq.\x ◘ \xo 1:20 \xt Řxř. 14:24; Yac. 14:13\x*
\b
\m 
\v 21 Ayt n Binyamin war zemmaren ad aẓẓřen x Iyabusiyyen, inni izeddɣen di Urcalim. Ammu i qqimen Iyabusiyyen zeddɣen ɣar ayt n Binyamin di Urcalim, ař ass-a.
\m 
\v 22 Taddart n Yusuf tgeɛɛed ɣar Bayt-Il uca SIDI \add tuɣa-t\add* akidsen.
\v 23 Tuyur taddart n Yusuf ḥima ad tbergag ɣar Bayt-Il. Isem n tendint \add tuɣa\add* zic qqaren as Luz. \x ◘ \xo 1:23 \xt Amz. 28:19\x*
\v 24 Inni tuɣa iřebten \add i tendint\add*, ẓrin ijj n weryaz iffeɣ-dd zi tendint, nnan as: “Scen aneɣ manis nzemmar ad nadef ɣar tendint, xenni neccin ad kik negg tamexsiwt icewwaren.”
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* isscen asen tawwart n wadaf ɣar tendint uca nitni wtin tandint s ict n tecti s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, \add maca\add* nitni jjin aryaz nni ad yuyur ak-d marra raǧ nnes.
\v 26 Uca yuyur weryaz ɣar temmurt n Iḥittiyyen uca ibna ict n tendint, igga as isem Luz. Wa d isem nnes ař ass-a.
\m 
\v 27 Manassa war izemmar ad yaẓẓeř x \add imezdaɣ\add* n Bayt-Can d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen, řa \add x imezdaɣ n\add* Taɛnak ak-d tneddam nnes řa x imezdaɣ n Dur d tneddam nnes řa x imezdaɣ n Yiblaɛam d tneddam nnes uřa x imezdaɣ n Majiddu d tneddam nnes. Tuɣa ayt n Kenɛan ɛewwřen ad qqimen zeddɣen di temmurt \add nni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 1:27 \xt Yac. 17:11, 12\x*
\v 28 Tuɣa Israil idweř ijhed ařami igga ljizya x ayt n Kenɛan, \add maca\add* war zemmaren ad xasen aẓẓřen marra.
\m 
\v 29 \add Uřa d\add* Ifrayim war izemmar ad yaẓẓeř x ayt n Kenɛan i tuɣa izeddɣen di Jazar u qqimen ayt n Kenɛan zeddɣen di řwesṭ nsen di Jazar. \x ◘ \xo 1:29 \xt Yac. 16:10\x*
\m 
\v 30 Zabulun war izemmar ad yaẓẓeř x imezdaɣ n Qiṭrun d imezdaɣ n Nahalul u qqimen ayt n Kenɛan zeddɣen di řwesṭ nsen u tᵉttwagg xasen ljizya.
\m 
\v 31 Acir war izemmar ad yaẓẓeř x imezdaɣ n Ɛakku uřa x \add imezdaɣ\add* n Ṣidun d Aḥlab d Akzib d Halba d Afiq d Raḥub.
\v 32 Iciriyyen zeddɣen di řwesṭ n ayt n Kenɛan, inni d imezdaɣ n temmurt, minzi nitni war zemmaren ad xasen aẓẓřen. \f ◼ \fr 1:32 \fk Iciriyyen\ft - ixs ad yini ‘ayt n Acir’.\f*
\m 
\v 33 Naftali war izemmar ad yaẓẓeř x imezdaɣ n Bayt-Cams d imezdaɣ n Bayt-Ɛanat. \add Ammu\add* i tuɣa izdeɣ di řwesṭ n ayt n Kenɛan, inni d imezdaɣ n temmurt. Tᵉttwagg xasen ljizya x imezdaɣ n Bayt-Cams d Bayt-Ɛanat.
\m 
\v 34 Imuriy\add yen\add* ḥṣaren ayt n Dan ɣar idurar, minzi war ten jjin ad hwan ɣar řewḍa n teɣzurt.
\v 35 Tuɣa Imuriy\add yen\add* ɛewwřen ad qqimen zeddɣen deg idurar n Ḥaras, di Ayalun u di Caɛalbim, \add maca\add* afus n taddart n Yusuf tuɣa izeyyar \add xasen\add* aṭṭas \add ařami xasen\add* tᵉttwagg ljizya.
\v 36 Tuɣa aymir n Imuriy\add yen\add* zi Tsunta n Tɣarḍmiwin, zi jjarf uca ssenni ɣar sennej.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Lmalak n SIDI di Bukim
\m 
\v 1 lmalak n SIDI igeɛɛed zi Jiljal ɣar Bukim, inna: “Necc ssuffɣeɣ-dd kenniw zi Miṣra uca iwyeɣ-dd kenniw ɣar temmurt nni x jjuǧeɣ i řejdud nwem, nniɣ: ‘Necc ɛemmarṣ war ttareẓẓiɣ Řɛahd inu akidwem i řebda. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Amz. 17:7; Aɛwd. 29:13, 14\x*
\v 2 Uca kenniw, war d awem iɛeddeř ad teggem uřa d ijj n řɛahd ak-d imezdaɣ n temmurt-a, u ittxeṣṣa awem ad tɣeḍřem iɛalṭaren nsen!’ Maca kenniw war tesřim ca i tmijja inu. Mayemmi teggim aya? \x ◘ \xo 2:2 \xt Aɛwd. 7:2; 12:3\x*
\v 3 U Necc nniɣ awem ɛawed: ‘Aqa war xasen taẓẓřeɣ zzat i wudem nwem, maca nitni ad iřin \add am isennanen\add* deg iɣezdisen nwem uca irebbiten nsen ad awem dewřen d řfex.’” \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Uf. 23:33; 34:12; Aɛwd. 7:16; Yac. 23:13\x*
\v 4 Umi lmalak n SIDI tuɣa issiweř awařen-a ɣar marra ayt n Israil, imsar, aqa řgens issgeɛɛed tmijja nnes uca run nitni.
\v 5 Nitni qqaren as i wemcan nni ‘Bukim’ uca nitni qeddmen din taɣarṣt i SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 2:5 \fk Bukim\ft - ixs ad yini ‘inni ittrun’.\f*
\b
\s1 Awarni i řmewt n Yacuwa iffeɣ ayt n Israil zeg webrid n SIDI
\m 
\v 6 \add Umi\add* issekk Yacuwa řgens, ffɣen ayt n Israil, \add kuř\add* aryaz ɣar tesɣart nnes, maḥend ad ṭṭfen tammurt d řwart. \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Yac. 24:28\x*
\v 7 Tuɣa řgens isexxar i SIDI marra ussan n Yacuwa d marra ussan n imɣaren, inni \add ɛad\add* iqqimen ddaren aṭṭas awarni i Yacuwa u inni iẓrin marra řxedmet tameqqrant n SIDI tenni igga i Israil.
\v 8 Yacuwa, mmis n Nun, amsexxar n SIDI, immut \add am\add* ijj n bnadem \add d bab\add* n mya u-ɛecra n iseggʷusa.
\v 9 Neḍřen t daxeř i weymir n tesɣart nnes di Timnat-Ḥaras, di temmurt n idurar n Ifrayim, ɣar uɣezdis n ccamal n wedrar n Jaɛac.
\m 
\v 10 U ɛawed marra jjiř nni, aqa ittwassmun ɣar řejdud nsen. Awarni asen ikkar-dd ijj n jjiř nneɣni, jjiř nni war issin ca SIDI u war issin ca řxedmet i igga ak-d Israil.
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* ggin ayt n Israil min tuɣa iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI uca sexxaren i ‘Ibaɛlen’
\v 12 Nitni jjin SIDI, AREBBI n řejdud nsen, wenni ten dd-issuffɣen zi Miṣra uca nitni ḍfaren irebbiten nneɣni, irebbiten n řegnus i d asen-dd innḍen, uca uḍaren asen u \add ammu i\add* sɛaren SIDI.
\v 13 Maɣar nitni jjin SIDI uca \add dewřen\add* sexxaren i Baɛal u i ‘Ɛactarutin’.
\v 14 \add X uya\add* yarɣa weɣḍab n SIDI x Israil. Netta igga i-ten deg ufus n iceffaren i ten ikeccḍen u igga i-ten deg ufus n řɛedyan nsen i d asen dd-innḍen uca dewřen war zemmaren ad \add qqimen\add* bedden zzat i wudem n řɛedyan nsen. \x ◘ \xo 2:14 \xt Izhd. 44:13; Ica. 50:1\x*
\v 15 Mani ma ffɣen nitni, tuɣa afus n SIDI ḍidd nsen i řɣar, am mammec tuɣa issiweř SIDI u am mammec tuɣa i d asen ijjuǧ SIDI. Aqa ttwaḥṣaren ař aneggar. \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Lawi 26; Aɛwd. 28\x*
\m 
\v 16 \add Maca\add* SIDI issekkar řquḍat, inni ten issnejmen zeg ufus n yinni ten ikeccḍen.
\v 17 Nitni war sřin ca uřa ɣar řquḍat nsen, maca ssfesden ixef nsen umi uyuren awarni irebbiten nneɣni uca uḍaren asen. Deɣya ḥeyyden x webrid nni i di uyuren řejdud nsen, inni tuɣa isřin i tweṣṣa n SIDI. Nitni \add maca\add* war ggin amenni!
\v 18 Umi d asen dd-issekkar SIDI řquḍat, tuɣa SIDI ak-d řqaḍi uca issenjem i-ten zeg ufus n řɛedyan nsen, marra ussan n řqaḍi nni, maɣar SIDI tuɣa indem zi ssibbet n iɣuyyan nsen zzat i wudem n yinni ten iḥṣaren d yinni i xasen ittaẓẓřen.
\v 19 Uca imsar umi immut řqaḍi, \add aqa\add* nitni dewřen ɣar ḍeffar uca dewřen ɛeffnen ktar zeg řejdud nsen umi uyuren awarni irebbiten nneɣni, sexxaren asen uca bendqen asen. Nitni war jjin zi tmegga nsen \add tiɛeffanin\add* u zi webrid nsen \add i tuɣa ḍeffaren\add* s tɣennant. \x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Řqḍ. 3:12\x*
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* yarɣa weɣḍab n SIDI x Israil uca Netta inna: “Minzi řgens-a iɛedda Řɛahd inu min xef weṣṣiɣ řejdud nsen u war sřin i tmijja inu,
\v 21 uřa d Necc war qqimeɣ ɛad ad aẓẓřeɣ zzat i wudem nsen x řegnus nni ijja Yacuwa, umi immut, \x ◘ \xo 2:21 \xt Yac. 23:13\x*
\v 22 ařami Necc ad zzaysen qeǧbeɣ Israil, ma ad ḥḍan nitni abrid n SIDI maḥend ad dayes uyuren am mammec t ḥḍan řejdud nsen, niɣ lla.”
\v 23 Uca ijja SIDI řegnus-a \add ad areyyḥen\add* uca war xasen yuẓẓiř deɣya u \add ɛawed\add* netta war ten iggi deg ufus n Yacuwa.
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Israil jar řegnus - Řquḍat
\m 
\v 1 Ina d řegnus i ijja SIDI \add ad areyyḥen\add*, ḥima ad zzaysen iqeǧeb Israil, \add ixs ad yini\add* marra inni war issinen ca ɛad x marra garrat ak-d Kenɛan,
\v 2 mɣir ḥima ad dewřen jjiřat n ayt n Israil ad ssnen amenɣi, ḥima ad řemden ad mmenɣen, mɣir inni war issinen ca amenɣi:
\v 3 xemsa n řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n ayt n Ifilisṭiniyyen d marra ayt n Kenɛan d Iṣiduniy\add yen\add* d Iḥiwiy\add yen\add* i izeddɣen x idurar n Lubnan, zeg wedrar n Baɛl-Hirmun ař mani ɣa tiwḍed ɣar Ḥamat.
\v 4 Nitni tuɣa aten \add din\add* ḥima ad zzaysen ittwaqeǧeb Israil, ḥima ad yiři ittwassnen ma nitni ad sřen i tweṣṣa n SIDI, tinni yumur Netta i řejdud nsen s tsexxart n Musa.
\m 
\v 5 Ayt n Israil tuɣa zeddɣen di řwesṭ n ayt n Kenɛan: Iḥittiy\add yen\add* d Imuriy\add yen\add* d Ifiriziy\add yen\add* d Iḥiwiy\add yen\add* d Iyabusiy\add yen\add*.
\v 6 Nitni iwyen yessitsen d temɣarin nsen i yixef nsen u tiḥenjirin nsen wcin tent i iḥenjiren nsen uca nitni \add bdan ad\add* sexxaren i irebbiten nsen. *
\b
\m 
\v 7 Uca ggin ayt n Israil min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, ttun SIDI, AREBBI nsen, uca uyuren ad sexxaren i ‘Ibaɛlen’ d tirebbin nsen n cwarti.
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* yarɣa weɣḍab n SIDI x Israil u Netta iwca i-ten deg ufus n Kucan-Ricaɛtayim, ajeǧid n Aram-Nahrayn, \add aqa-tt d Misuputamya\add*. \add Xenni\add* sexxaren ayt n Israil tmenya n iseggʷusa i Kucan-Ricaɛtayim.
\v 9 Sɣuyyen ayt n Israil ɣar SIDI uca SIDI igga ad ikkar ijj n umsenjem i ayt n Israil, wenni i ten ifekken, \bd Ɛutniyil\bd*, mmis n Qanaz, umas n Kalib, wenni d ameẓyan xas.
\v 10 Tuɣa xas Arruḥ n SIDI u tuɣa d řqaḍi x Israil uca iffeɣ ɣar umenɣi. Iwca as SIDI Kucan-Ricaɛtayim, ajeǧid n Aram, deg ufus nnes uca iɣřeb netta x Kucan-Ricaɛtayim.
\v 11 Tareyyeḥ temmurt arebɛin n iseggʷusa. \add Xenni\add* immut Ɛutniyil, mmis n Qanaz.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Ayt n Israil arnin ad ggen min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Uca SIDI igga jjehd di Ɛijlun, ajeǧid n Mu’ab, ḍidd i Israil, minzi nitni ggin \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.
\v 13 Netta issmun ɣares ayt n Ɛammun u n Ɛamaliq uca iffeɣ, iɣřeb x Israil uca nitni ṭṭfen Tandint n Tcejjura n Tini. \f ◼ \fr 3:13 \fk Tandint n Tcejjura n Tini\ft - ixs ad yini ‘Ariḥa’.\f*
\v 14 Tmenṭac n iseggʷusa tuɣa ayt n Israil ttsexxaren i Ɛijlun, ajeǧid n Mu’ab.
\m 
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* sɣuyen ayt n Israil ɣar SIDI uca SIDI igga ad dd-ikkar ijj n umsenjem, \bd Ihud\bd*, mmis n Jira, \add zi teqbič\add* n Binyamin, ijj n weryaz i war ittwadarreb mliḥ s ufusi nnes afusi. Uca ayt n Israil ssekken t ḥima ad wcen ict n terzeft i Ɛijlun, ajeǧid n Mu’ab, s ufus nnes.
\v 16 Ihud igga i yixef nnes ijj n ssif ɣares tnayen n řeqduɛ, tuzzeggart nnes anect n ijj n uɣiř, iqqen i-t sadu warruḍ nnes ɣar tmeṣṣaḍt nnes tafusect.
\v 17 Ammu i dd-iqarreb s terzeft ɣar Ɛijlun, ajeǧid n ayt n Mu’ab, Ɛijlun tuɣa d aryaz iṣeḥḥ aṭṭas.
\v 18 Umi tuɣa Ihud ikemmeř timewca n tarzeft, imsar, aqa issqebbeḍ iwdan i tuɣa yarebbun tarzeft \add ɣar řaggʷaj\add*,
\v 19 maca netta simant nnes iɛqeb \add awarni man aya\add* zi řexyař ineqcen \add i din iǧan\add* di Jiljal, inna: “Necc ɣari ijj n ssir xak, ajeǧid!” Uca wa inna: “Sqarem!” Marra wi tuɣa ibedden ɣares, ffɣen zi ɣares \add ɣar barra\add*.
\m 
\v 20 Yusa-dd ɣares Ihud umi Ɛijlun iqqim deg wexxam n nnej asemmaḍ, wenni tuɣa i netta waha. \add Xenni\add* inna Ihud: “Necc ɣari ijj n wawař n AREBBI i cek.” Uca ikkar \add ujeǧid\add* zi řkursi nnes igellden.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* isswiẓẓeḍ Ihud s ufus nnes azeřmaḍ, ijbed-dd ssif nni x tmeṣṣaḍt nnes tafusect, icukk i-t deg uɛeddis nnes,
\v 22 ařami yudef s ufus nni awarni i řmus n ssif uca tadunt tbelleɛ-dd x řmus, maɣar netta war ikkis ssif zeg uɛeddis nnes. \add Xas uca\add* iffeɣ s webrid n wexxam n yiḍeṣ.
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ Ihud zeg wuffuɣ \add n wexxam n wesqif\add*. Ibelleɛ tiwwura n wexxam n nnej awarni as u yarra zzekrun.
\m 
\v 24 \add Umi\add* yuyur netta, usin-dd imsexxaren nnes uca umi ẓrin aqa tiwwura n wexxam n nnej ttwabellɛent s zzekrun, nnan: “Netta aqa idřa \add waha\add* iḍaren nnes deg wexxam asemmaḍ n daxeř.”
\v 25 Nitni qqimen ttrajan ařami dewřen sseṣḥan, u xzar, netta war yarzim ca tiwwura n wexxam n nnej. Nitni ksin ssarut, arzmen tawwart, uca xzar, immenḍar siditsen ɣar temmurt immut.
\m 
\v 26 Ihud \add maca\add* tuɣa yarweř, am tuɣa ttrajan nitni. Netta tuɣa ikka x řexyař ineqcen uca yarweř ɣar Siɛirat.
\v 27 Řami dd-yiweḍ netta \add dinni\add*, isuḍ deg uyicc n icarri x idurar n Ifrayim. \add Xenni\add* hwan ayt n Israil akides zeg wedrar u netta simant nnes \add yuyur\add* zzat i wudem nsen.
\v 28 Netta inna asen: “Ḍfarem ayi-dd, minzi SIDI iwca awem řɛedyan nwem, ayt n Mu’ab, deg ufus nwem.” Uca nitni ḍfaren t uca ṭṭfen imucan n uẓekkwu n L’Urdun ɣar Mu’ab uca war jjin uřa d ijj ad iẓwa.
\v 29 Di řweqt nni wtin nitni ayt n Mu’ab, ɛřaḥař tenɛac-ařef n yeryazen, marra nitni jehden, iɛeskariyyen, uřa d ijj n weryaz war injim.
\v 30 \add Ammu\add* ittwassdeǧ Mu’ab deg wass nni sadu ufus n Israil uca tareyyeḥ temmurt tmenyin n iseggʷusa.
\b
\m 
\v 31 Awarni as yusa-dd \bd Camjar\bd*, mmis n Ɛanat, wenni inɣin setta-mya n yeryazen zeg Ifilisṭiniyyen s yijj n řmacam n ifunasen. \add Ammu\add* issenjem uřa d \bd netta\bd* Israil.
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Aɣelleb n Baraq d Dabura
\m 
\v 1 Umi tuɣa Ihud immut, arnin ayt n Israil ad ggen min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.
\v 2 SIDI igga i-ten SIDI deg ufus n Yabin, ajeǧid n ayt n Kenɛan, wenni tuɣa iḥekkem di Ḥaṣur. Tuɣa Sisara d akumandar n řɛeskar nnes. Wa tuɣa izeddɣen di Harucit-ha-Xuyim. \x ◘ \xo 4:2 \xt 1 Ṣm. 12:9\x*
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* sɣuyen ayt n Israil i SIDI, maɣar Sisara ɣares tesɛa-mya n ikarruten n uzzař i umenɣi u netta tuɣa issdeǧ ayt n Israil s lɛunf \add řmijař n\add* ɛicrin n iseggʷusa.
\v 4 Tuɣa \bd Dabura\bd*, tanabit, ict n temɣart s arruḥ am tmessi, teḥkem Israil di řweqt nni.
\v 5 \bd Nettat\bd* tuɣa tᵉqqim \add x řkursi n řḥukm\add* swadday i tcejjart n tini n Dabura, jar Rama d Bayt-Il, x idurar n Ifrayim, uca ayt n Israil geɛɛden ɣares maḥend ad as awyen ddeɛwat \add nsen\add*.
\v 6 Nettat tessekk, třaɣa i \bd Baraq\bd*, mmis n Abinuɛam zi Qadac di Naftali, tenna as: “Ma war yumur SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Uyur, ffeɣ ɣar wedrar n Tabur u tawyed akidek ɛecra ařef n yeryazen zeg ayt n Naftali u zeg ayt n Zabulun! \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt Ɛbr. 11:32\x*
\v 7 Ɣar teɣzart n Qicun necc ad ɣarek nedheɣ Sisara, akumandar n řɛeskar n Yabin, ak-d ikarruten nnes d ubarru nnes \add n yeryazen\add* uca ad ac t-i-dd-wceɣ deg ifassen nnec!’” \x ◘ \xo 4:7 \xt Izhd. 83:10\x*
\v 8 Baraq inna as: “Mařa cem tuyured akidi, ad uyureɣ, \add maca\add* mařa cem war kidi tuyured, war ggureɣ.”
\v 9 Nettat tenna: “Necc ad kik uyureɣ nican, mɣir war d ac ittiři ccan deg webrid i ɣa tuyured, minzi SIDI ad izzenz Sisara ɣar ufus n ict temɣart.” \add Xenni\add* tekkar Dabura uca tuyur ak-d Baraq ɣar Qadac.
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* Baraq iřaɣa-dd i Zabulun d Naftali ɣar Qadac uca igeɛɛed x iḍaren ak-d ɛecra-ařaf n yeryazen uca uřa d Dabura tuyur akides.
\m 
\v 11 Ḥabir, Aqini, wenni tuɣa ittnejřa x Qayin, netta \add d ijj n\add* zeg ayt n Ḥubab, aḍeggʷař n Musa. Aqa iwta iqiḍan nnes ɣar tcejjart n yigg di Ṣaɛanayim nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar Qadac. \x ◘ \xo 4:11 \xt Řxř. 10:29\x*  *
\b
\m 
\v 12 Xebbaren i Sisara, aqa Baraq, mmis n Abinuɛam, igeɛɛed ɣar wedrar n Tabur.
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* issmun-dd Sisara marra ikarruten nnes, tesɛa-mya n ikarruten n wuzzař, d marra řgens i tuɣa ɣares iǧan, zi Ḥarucat-ha-Xuyim ař teɣzart n Qicun.
\m 
\v 14 Uca tenna Dabura i Baraq: “Kkar, minzi wa d ass i di iwca SIDI Sisara deg ufus nnec. Ma war dd-itteffeɣ SIDI \add simant nnes\add* ɣar zzat i cek!” \add Xenni\add* ihwa-dd Baraq zeg wedrar n Tabur u ɛecra-ařaf n yeryazen ḍfaren t.
\v 15 SIDI yaẓẓeř x Sisara u x marra ikarruten nnes u x marra řɛeskar nnes s řeqḍeɛ n ssif zzat i wudem n Baraq, \add ařami\add* iḍra x ukarru, yarweř x iḍaren. \x ◘ \xo 4:15 \xt Izhd. 83:10\x*
\v 16 Uca Baraq iḍfar ikarruten d řɛeskar ař Ḥarucat-ha-Xuyim. Marra řɛeskar n Sisara iwḍa s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, ařami war iqqim uřa d ijj.
\m 
\v 17 Sisara yarweř x iḍaren ɣar uqiḍun n Yaɛil, tamɣart n Ḥabir, Aqini, maɣar tuɣa řehna jar Yabin, ajeǧid n Ḥaṣur d taddart n Ḥabir, Aqini.
\v 18 Yaɛil teffeɣ ɣar Sisara, tenna as: “Ejj abrid, \add a\add* sidi inu, ejj abrid ɣari, war tteggʷed!” Uca netta iffeɣ \add zeg webrid\add*, \add yuyur\add* ɣares ɣar uqiḍun uca nettat tedřa i-t s ict n tmaltat.
\v 19 Netta inna as: “Ewc ayi aman ad sweɣ, necc dayi afadi!” Nettat tarzem ict n txancet n uɣi u tewca as ad isu, xenni tedřa i-t \add twařat nneɣnit\add*. \x ◘ \xo 4:19 \xt Řqḍ. 5:25\x*
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* inna as ɛawed: “Bedd ɣar tewwart n uqiḍun uca mařa yusa-dd ijjen isseqsa \add cem\add*, iqqar: ‘Ma da ca n ijj?’, xenni arr xas: ‘Uřa d ijj!’”
\v 21 Teṭṭef Yaɛil, tamɣart n Ḥabir, ijj n řewted n uqiḍun uca teksi ijj n wefḍis deg ufus nnes uca tudef ɣares nhřa řḥess uca tewta as řewted deg uɣezdis \add n uzeǧif\add* nnes ařami yiweḍ \add řewted\add* ɣar temmurt. Tuɣa netta yuǧeɣ deg yiḍeṣ s řweḥřan, uca \add ammu i\add* immut.
\m 
\v 22 U xzar, Baraq tuɣa iḍeffar Sisara uca teffeɣ Yaɛil, truḥ ad kis temmeřqa, tenna as: “As-dd, ad ac ssecneɣ aryaz wenni x tarezzud!” Netta yudef akides uca aqa Sisara ittazzeř \add x temmurt\add* u řewted di lḥenk \add n uzeǧif\add* nnes.
\v 23 Ammu i ideǧ SIDI Yabin, ajeǧid n Kenɛan, zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil deg wass nni.
\v 24 Afus n ayt n Israil yarenni ad iṭṭef uca idqeř aṭṭas x Yabin, ajeǧid n Kenɛan, ařami tuɣa teḥḥan Yabin, ajeǧid n Kenɛan.
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Izři n uɣelleb n Dabura d Baraq
\m 
\v 1 Deg wass nni ɣennjen Dabura d Baraq, mmis n Abinuɛam, nnan:
\b
\m 
\v 2 \qt “Barkem SIDI i ijeṭṭayen\qt*
\m \qt n ucuwwaf ittwafessyen di Israil\qt*,
\m \qt s uṭewweɛ n řgens s řxaḍar!\qt*
\m 
\v 3 \qt Sřem, \tl kenniw,\tl* ijeǧiden,\qt*
\m \qt sḥessem, \tl kenniw,\tl* ayt n jjehd!\qt*
\m \qt Necc ad ɣennjeɣ izřan i SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt necc ad zehhdeɣ i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 4 \qt \tl A\tl* SIDI, umi Cek dd-teffɣed zi Saɛir,\qt*
\m \qt umi Cek tuɣa teggured zeg iyyar n Idum,\qt*
\m \qt tenhezz temmurt, yarjij ujenna,\qt*
\m \qt \tl wah,\tl* uřa d iseynuten farrɣen-dd s waman.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 5:4 \xt Izhd. 68:8, 9\x*
\m 
\v 5 \qt Idurar fesyen zzat i wudem n SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt adrar nni n Sina, \tl ifsi\tl*\qt*
\m \qt zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.\qt* \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Uf. 19:18; Izhd. 68:15, 16, 17; 97:5\x*
\m 
\v 6 \qt Deg wussan n Camjar, mmis n Ɛanat,\qt*
\m \qt deg wussan n Yaɛil, qqimen ibriden xřan,\qt*
\m \qt u inni tuɣa igguren x tebridin,\qt*
\m \qt ttekken imesraq iɛarrqen.\qt*
\m 
\v 7 \qt Imjaheden war qqimen,\qt*
\m \qt war qqimen di Israil,\qt*
\m \qt ařami kkareɣ necc, Dabura,\qt*
\m \qt ařami kkareɣ necc, yemmas n Israil.\qt*
\m 
\v 8 \qt Umi ifarz \tl řgens\tl* irebbiten nneɣni,\qt*
\m \qt \tl xenni\tl* tuɣa din ijj n umenɣi ineqqen\qt*
\m \qt ɣar tewwura.\qt*
\m \qt Taseddart n uɛeskar d uḥric,\qt*
\m \qt war ittwaẓri ɛad jar arebɛa-ařaf\qt*
\m \qt di Israil!\qt*
\m 
\v 9 \qt Uř inu ak-d imgewwaden n Israil,\qt*
\m \qt inni iṭewwɛen ixef nsen jar řgens s řxaḍar,\qt*
\m \qt lbaraka i SIDI!\qt*
\m 
\v 10 \qt \tl A kenniw\tl*, inni innayen\qt*
\m \qt x teɣyař d ticemřařin,\qt*
\m \qt \tl kenniw\tl* inni ittɣiman x tzarbiyyin\qt*
\m \qt d \tl kenniw\tl* inni igguren deg webrid,\qt*
\m \qt siwřem \tl x man aya\tl*!\qt*
\m 
\v 11 \qt S tmijja n imjebbaden n řqews\qt*
\m \qt i din jar wanuten,\qt*
\m \qt aqa ittwaseř wawař\qt*
\m \qt x tmegga iseggden n SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt timegga iseggden n umjahad n Israil.\qt*
\m \qt \tl Xenni\tl* ihwa-dd řgens n SIDI\qt*
\m \qt ɣar tewwura \tl n tendint\tl*.\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 12 \qt Ḥḍat, ḥḍat, Dabura,\qt*
\m \qt ḥḍat, ḥḍat, siweř s yijj n izři!\qt*
\m \qt Kkar, Baraq, awi imeḥbas nnec,\qt*
\m \qt a cek, mmis n Abinuɛam!\qt*
\m 
\v 13 \qt Xenni ihwa \tl kuř\tl* wi yarewřen\qt*
\m \qt ɣar ayt n jjehd n řgens,\qt*
\m \qt SIDI ihwa-dd ɣari ak-d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt.\qt*
\m 
\v 14 \qt Zeg Ifrayim usin-dd\qt*
\m \qt \tl inni\tl* aẓwar nsen di Ɛamaliq\qt*
\m \qt u awarni ac yuyur Binyamin\qt*
\m \qt jar \tl řɛeskarat n\tl* yewdan nnec.\qt*
\m \qt Zi Maxir hwan imgewwaden,\qt*
\m \qt u zi Zabulun inni iṭṭfen\qt*
\m \qt aɛekkaz n wenni iḥessben.\qt*
\m 
\v 15 \qt Řḥukkam n Issakar \tl hwan-dd\tl* ak-d Dabura,\qt*
\m \qt uca am mammec \tl ittwassekk\tl* Issaxar,\qt*
\m \qt ammu i ittwassekk uřa d Baraq\qt*
\m \qt di řewḍa n teɣzurt.\qt*
\m \qt Di řeṣfuf n Rubin\qt*
\m \qt tuɣa ixarriṣen n wuř d aṭṭas.\qt*
\m 
\v 16 \qt Mayemmi teqqimed jar iɣendifen,\qt*
\m \qt tessḥessed ɣar wesbuɛriy n tḥimriwin?\qt*
\m \qt Di řeṣfuf n Rubin\qt*
\m \qt ggin ad beqqcendeg wuř aṭṭas.\qt*
\m 
\v 17 \qt Jilɛad iqqim izeddeɣ\qt*
\m \qt x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun\qt*
\m \qt u mayemmi iqqim Dan ɣar tɣarruba?\qt*
\m \qt Acir iqqim ɣar tma n řebḥar\qt*
\m \qt uca \tl iqqim\tl* izdeɣ ɣar iftasen nnes.\qt*
\m 
\v 18 \qt Zabulun d ijj n řgens\qt*
\m \qt isebbeř tudart nnes ař řmewt,\qt*
\m \qt am \tl t igga\tl* uřa d Naftali\qt*
\m \qt x řegɛudi n wazzay \tl n umenɣi\tl*.\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 19 \qt Ijeǧiden usin-dd, mmenɣen.\qt*
\m \qt Řexdenni mmenɣen ijeǧiden n Kenɛan\qt*
\m \qt di Taɛnak ɣar waman n Majiddu,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* war ksin takeccaḍt n nnuqart.\qt*
\m 
\v 20 \qt \tl Minzi\tl* itran mmenɣen zeg ujenna,\qt*
\m \qt mmenɣen ak-d Sisara zi tebridin nsen.\qt*
\m 
\v 21 \qt Iɣzar n Qicun iwyi i-ten,\qt*
\m \qt tiɣzart n mecḥař uya, tiɣzart n Qicun!\qt*
\m \qt Uyur s jjehd, \tl a\tl* řeɛmar inu.\qt*
\m 
\v 22 \qt Řexdenni nnxuxřent ticeḍyin n iysan\qt*
\m \qt zeg urabeɛ břa uqeṭṭu\qt*
\m \qt zeg ayt n bu-ṣṣulṭa nnes.\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 23 \qt Neɛřem Miruz, inna lmalak n SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt neɛřem imezdaɣ nnes s \tl ict n\tl* nneɛřet,\qt*
\m \qt minzi war dd-usin\qt*
\m \qt ḥima ad wcen afus i SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt \tl ḥima\tl* ad wcen afus i SIDI\qt*
\m \qt s ayt n bu-teɣruḍt \tl nsen\tl*.\qt*
\m 
\v 24 \qt Tettwabarek Yaɛil, tamɣart n Ḥabir, Aqini,\qt*
\m \qt sennej i \tl marra\tl* timɣarin.\qt*
\m \qt Tettwabarek nettat sennej\qt*
\m \qt i marra timɣarin \tl izeddɣen\tl* deg iqiḍan.\qt*
\m 
\v 25 \qt Netta ittar aman, nettat tewca as aɣi,\qt*
\m \qt tiwi \tl as-dd\tl* trussi\qt*
\m \qt deg ict n ṭṭebṣi d ameqqran aṭṭas.\qt*
\m 
\v 26 \qt S ufus nnes tesswiẓẓeḍ ɣar řewted,\qt*
\m \qt afus afusi nnes ɣar wefḍis n ixeddamen.\qt*
\m \qt Nettat tewta Sisara,\qt*
\m \qt texbeḍ as x uzeǧif nnes,\qt*
\m \qt teřbez uca tessnuqqeb as\qt*
\m \qt aɣezdis \tl n uzeǧif\tl* nnes.\qt*
\m 
\v 27 \qt Ikmummec jar iḍaren nnes,\qt*
\m \qt ibbuzzeř, aqa izzeř \tl din\tl*.\qt*
\m \qt Aqa ikmummec jar iḍaren nnes, ibbuzzeř.\qt*
\m \qt Umi tuɣa ittekmummuc,\qt*
\m \qt iwḍa din, uca iwḍa-dd iřeqqef!\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 28 \qt Zi řkazi \tl nnes\tl* texzar-dd yemmas n Sisara\qt*
\m \qt uca tesɣuy jar iqḍiben n wuzzař\qt*
\m \qt ‘Mayemmi iɛeṭṭař ukarru nnes n umenɣi\qt*
\m \qt ammu aṭṭas?\qt*
\m \qt Mayemmi iɛeṭṭař ddriz n ikarruten nnes’\qt*
\m 
\v 29 \qt Inni d tiɣmisin aṭṭas jar tjeǧidin nnes\qt*
\m \qt arrint-i-dd,\qt*
\m \qt \tl uca\tl* uřa d nettat simant nnes\qt*
\m \qt tarra-dd x min tenna:\qt*
\m 
\v 30 \qt ‘Ma \tl xenni nitni\tl* war ufin walu\qt*
\m \qt uca aqa aten war beṭṭin takeccaḍt?\qt*
\m \qt I kuř aryaz ijehden ict \tl n teɛzarect\tl*\qt*
\m \qt niɣ tnayen \tl n teɛzariyyin\tl*?\qt*
\m \qt Takeccaḍt n \tl ikettanen\tl* ittwassqareqcen\qt*
\m \qt i Sisara,\qt*
\m \qt takeccaḍt n \tl ikettanen\tl* ittwassqareqcen,\qt*
\m \qt aburḍa, řxedmet n umudi\qt*
\m \qt ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen\qt*
\m \qt zeg ukettan ittwassqareqcen i irawen,\qt*
\m \qt am tkeccaḍt?’\qt*
\b
\m 
\v 31 \qt Ammu i ɣa hellken řɛedyan nnec, \tl a\tl* SIDI,\qt*
\m \qt \tl maca\tl* inni Cek ittexsen ad iřin am tfuct\qt*
\m \qt i dd-ineqqaren di jjehd nnes.”\qt*
\b
\m \add Awarni aya\add* tareyyeḥ temmurt arebɛin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 5:31 \xt Izhd. 19:6\x*
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Jidɛun d Lmalak n SIDI
\m 
\v 1 \add Maca\add* ayt n Israil ggin min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI uca isellem i-ten SIDI deg ufus n Midyan, \add ijj n řmijař n\add* sebɛa n iseggʷusa.
\v 2 \add Umi\add* tuɣa afus n Midyan ijhed x Israil, ggin ayt n Israil i yixef nsen ifran deg idurar d ixerdusen d lqelɛat ḍidd i Midyan.
\v 3 \add Awarni řami\add* tuɣa zarrɛen ayt n Israil, ttgeɛɛed Midyan uca uřa d ayt n Ɛamaliq d ayt n ccarq ttgeɛɛden ḍidd nsen.
\v 4 Nitni wtin iqiḍan nsen ḍidd nsen uca areddǧen řɣiǧet n temmurt ař \add jjwayeh\add* n Ɣazza. Nitni war jjin di Israil i zi ɣa iddar \add bnadem\add*, řa d uǧi, řa d afunas uřa d aɣyuř.
\v 5 Maɣar nitni geɛɛden s tḥimriwin nsen d iqiḍan nsen uca usin-dd am yijj n weyřaf n tmurɣi. War izemmar ad ttwaḥesben ak-d iřeɣman nsen uca nitni udfen ɣar tammurt, ḥima ad tt areddǧen.
\v 6 \add Ammu\add* iẓřeḍ Israil aṭṭas zi ssibbet n Midyan. Uca \add xenni\add* sɣuyen ayt n Israil ɣar SIDI.
\m 
\v 7 Xmi sɣuyen ayt n Israil ɣar SIDI di ssibbet n Midyan, imsar,
\v 8 aqa SIDI issekk-dd ijj n weryaz, ijj n unabi, ɣar ayt n Israil. Netta inna asen: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘\bd Necc\bd* ssgeɛɛdeɣ kenniw zi Miṣra u ssuffɣeɣ-dd kenniw zi taddart n tesmuɣi.
\v 9 Necc fekkeɣ-dd kenniw zeg ufus n Imiṣriyyen u zeg ufus n marra inni kenniw iḥṣaren. Necc uẓẓřeɣ xasen zzat i wudem nwem u wciɣ awem tammurt nsen.
\v 10 Necc nniɣ awem: Necc d SIDI, AREBBI nwem, war ttɛebbdem irebbiten n Imuriyyen, inni di temmurt nsen tzeddɣem!’ \add Maca\add* kenniw war tesřim ɣar tmijja inu.” \x ◘ \xo 6:10 \xt 2 Ij. 17:35, 38\x*
\m 
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd lmalak n SIDI uca iqqim sadu n tcejjura n yigg nni iǧan ɣar Ɛafra, tenni n Yuwac, Abiɛazari. Mmis \bd Jidɛun\bd* tuɣa-t \add din\add* issarwat irden di tsirt n uḍiř ḥima ad t issarweř ammu zzat i wudem n Midyan. \f ◼ \fr 6:11 \fk Yuwac\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘wenni immewcen s ufus n Arebbi’.\f*
\m 
\v 12 \add Řexdenni\add* iban as-dd lmalak n SIDI, inna as: “SIDI akidek, a cek, bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen!”
\v 13 Jidɛun inna as: “A, Sidi inu, mařa SIDI aqa-t akidneɣ, mayemmi i d aneɣ iřqef \add xenni\add* marra uya u mani ǧan marra řeɛjayeb i x d aneɣ ssiwřen řejdud nneɣ, umi nitni nnan: ‘Ma war d aneɣ-dd issuffeɣ SIDI zi Miṣra?’ Maca řexxu inḍar aneɣ SIDI, isellem aneɣ deg ifassen n Midyan.”
\v 14 \add Rexdenni\add* idweř-dd ɣares SIDI, inna: “Uyur di jjehd nnec wanita uca ad tfekked Israil zeg ufus n Midyan. Ma Necc war cek-dd ssekkeɣ?” \x ◘ \xo 6:14 \xt 1 Ṣm. 12:11; Ɛbr. 11:32\x*
\v 15 \add Maca\add* netta yarra-dd xas: “A Sidi inu, s minzi i ɣa fekkeɣ Israil? Xzar řwacun inu d tamezřuḍt qaɛ di Manassa u necc d amudrus qaɛ di taddart n baba.”
\v 16 Inna as SIDI: “Minzi Necc ad iřiɣ akidek, ad tɣeřbed Midyan, axmi d ijj n weryaz waha.”
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* inna as netta: “Mařa \add xenni\add* ufiɣ arḍa di tiṭṭawin nnec, \add xenni\add* iwca ayi ict n řeɛřamet, aqa d Cek simant nnec i kidi issawařen.
\v 18 War ssa ttraḥ ca, ař ɣarek dd ɣa ɛeqbeɣ ad tiři iwyeɣ-dd tewhibt inu u ad tt-i-dd-ssarseɣ zzatek.” Netta inna: “Ad qqimeɣ ař dd ɣa tɛeqbed.”
\m 
\v 19 Uca yudef Jidɛun, issewjed ijj n iɣayḍ d ameẓyan zeg iɣayḍen d iɣrumen břa aɣrum zeg yijj n ifa n waren. Netta issars aysum di tṣuǧet, igga arrwa deg ict n teydurt uca yiwi \add man aya\add* ɣares ɣar barra sadu tcejjart n yigg uca issars as \add man aya\add*.
\v 20 \add Maca\add* inna as lmalak n AREBBI: “Ksi aysum d iɣrumen břa antun u tessarsed ten \add da\add* x teṣḍart uca zeǧeɛ xas arrwa!” Uca ammu i t igga.
\v 21 \add Xas\add* uca isarreḥ lmalak n SIDI tixeft n teɣɣarct i tuɣa ɣares deg ufus, iḥada zzayes aysum d iɣrumen břa antun. \add Řexdenni\add* tgeɛɛed tmessi zi teṣḍart, tecca aysum d iɣrumen. \add Xenni\add* innufseř lmalak n SIDI x tiṭṭawin n Jidɛun.
\m 
\v 22 \add Umi\add* Jidɛun iẓra, aqa tuɣa-t d lmalak n SIDI, inna Jidɛun: “A, Sidi inu, SIDI, aqa necc ẓriɣ lmalak n SIDI aɣembub deg uɣembub.”
\v 23 \add Maca\add* SIDI yarra-dd xas: “\add Ad\add* kidek \add yiři\add* řehna, war tteggʷed ca, cek war ttmettid.”
\v 24 Uca Jidɛun ibna dinni ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI, igga as: “SIDI d řehna!” Aqa-t di Ɛafra n \add ayt n\add* Abiɛazari ař ass-a.
\b
\m 
\v 25 Di ǧiřet nni simant nnes, imsar aqa SIDI inna as: “Ksi ijj n ufunas ameẓyan zeg ifunasen \add i iǧan\add* n babac, aqa afunas ameẓyan wiss tnayen n sebɛa n iseggʷusa uca ɣḍeř aɛalṭar n Baɛl \add i iǧan\add* n babac u zdem tarebbit n cwarti nni zzates!
\v 26 Bna \add xenni\add* ijj n uɛalṭar i SIDI, AREBBI nnec, x tqiccat n lqelɛa-ya, sewjed i-t, uca ksi afunas ameẓyan wiss tnayen uca awyi t-i-dd d tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ s ukeccuḍ n trebbit n cwarti nni ittxeṣṣa ad tzedmed.”
\m 
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* iksi Jidɛun ɛecra n yeryazen zeg imsexxaren nnes uca igga am mammec d as inna SIDI. \add Maca\add* umi netta iggʷed zi \add řwacun\add* n taddart n babas u zeg yeryazen n tendint ad t igg s wass, igga i-t di ǧiřet.
\v 28 Umi dd-kkaren yeryazen n tendint tiwecca zic, ẓrin nitni aqa aɛalṭar n Baɛl ittwahdem uca tᵉttwazdem trebbit n cwarti nni zzates u afunas ameẓyan wiss tnayen ittwabexxar x uɛalṭar i \add din\add* ittwabnan.
\v 29 Uca nnan i wayawya: “Man wen iggin aya?” Nitni sseqsan, arzun uca nnan: “Jidɛun, mmis n Yuwac, i-t iggin.”
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* nnan yeryazen n tendint i Yuwac: “Sufeɣ-dd mmic \add ḥima\add* ad immet, minzi netta iɣḍer aɛalṭar n Baɛl u minzi netta izdem tarebbit n cwarti i zzates \add iǧan\add*.”
\v 31 Yuwac yarra-dd x marra inni i dd ɣares ibedden: “Ma texsem ad tmenɣem i Baɛl? Ma texsem ad t tessnejmem? Wenni akides i ɣa ibedden, ad ittwaneɣ di ṣṣbeḥ-a wanita. Mařa netta d ijj n arebbi, ejj i-t ad immneɣ i yixef nnes nnit, minzi ɣeḍřen aɛalṭar nnes.”
\v 32 Deg wass nni iřaɣa as-dd \add i Jidɛun\add* Yarubbaɛl, min ixs ad yini: “Baɛl immneɣ akides, maɣar netta iɣḍeř aɛalṭar nnes.”
\b
\m 
\v 33 Marra Midyan d Ɛamaliq d ayt n ccarq munen uca ẓwan-dd \add L’Urdun\add* uca wtin iqiḍan nsen di řewḍa n teɣzurt n Yazraɛil.
\v 34 Arruḥ n SIDI issyarḍ i Jidɛun uca netta isuḍ deg uyicc n icarri uca iřaɣa-dd x ayt n Abiɛazar maḥend \add ad bedden\add* awarni as.
\v 35 Issekk ireqqasen di marra Manassa uca ittwařaɣa Manassa \add maḥend ad bedden nitni\add* awarni as. Xenni issekk ireqqasen ɣar Acir u ɣar Zabulun u ɣar Naftali uca nitni geɛɛden maḥend ad ten mmeřqan.
\m 
\v 36 \add Xas\add* uca inna Jidɛun i AREBBI: “Mařa Cek texsed \add s tidett\add* ad tfekked Israil s ufus inu am mammec i d ayi tennid,
\v 37 xzar, \add xenni\add* necc ad ssarseɣ \bd tahiḍurt n taḍuft x unedrar\bd*. Mařa iwḍa nnda mɣir x taḍuft waha, \add maca\add* tammurt marra \add teqqim\add* tuẓeɣ, \add xenni\add* ssneɣ necc, aqa Cek ad tessnejmed Israil s ufus inu, am mammec i d ayi tennid.”
\v 38 U ammu i temsar. Tiwecca nnes ikkar zic uca izři tahiḍurt uca iẓemm-dd nnda zi thiḍurt, ict n ṭṭawya teccur s waman.
\m 
\v 39 \add Xas uca\add* inna Jidɛun i AREBBI: “Ttzawgeɣ war xafi yareqq weɣḍab nnec mařa necc ssiwřeɣ ict n twařa nneɣnit. Ejj ayi ad qeǧbeɣ s thiḍurt \add ɛad\add* ict n twařa nneɣni waha, uca ad teqqim thiḍurt tuẓeɣ u x marra tammurt \add ad din yiři\add* nnda.” \x ◘ \xo 6:39 \xt Amz. 18:32\x*
\v 40 Uca di ǧiřet nni igga \add i-t\add* SIDI ammu: tahiḍurt waha i iqqimen tuẓeɣ u tuɣa nnda x marra tammurt.
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Jidɛun yaẓẓeř x ayt n Midyan
\m 
\v 1 Yarubbaɛl, wa d Jidɛun, ikkar zic uřa d marra řgens i ɣares iǧan uca wtin nitni řmargeḥ n řɛeskar nsen ɣar tařa n Ḥarud. Řmargeḥ n Midyan tuɣa iǧan zzates ɣar ccamal, zi tewrirt n Mura di řewḍa n teɣzurt.
\v 2 SIDI inna i Jidɛun: “Řgens i ɣarek \add iǧan\add* aqa-t deg waṭṭas. Ammu war zemmareɣ ad asen ggeɣ Midyan deg ufus nsen, niɣ izemmar Israil ad xafi ifeyyec ad yini: ‘Afus inu issenjem ayi.’
\v 3 S uya, řaɣa deg imezzuɣen n řgens, ini: ‘Wenni itteggʷeden d wenni ittarjijen ad iɛqeb uca ad iffeɣ deɣya zeg idurar n Jilɛad!’” \add Xenni\add* ɛeqben tnayen u-ɛicrin-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* zi řgens uca qqimen \add ɣares\add* ɛecra-ařaf. \x ◘ \xo 7:3 \xt Aɛwd. 20:8\x*
\v 4 \add Maca\add* SIDI inna i Jidɛun: “Řgens aqa-t ɛad deg waṭṭas. Sehwa ten ɣar waman, dinni ad ten ddzeɣ i cek. Ad imsar x wenni i d ac ɣa iniɣ: ‘Wa ad kik iraḥ!’, win ad kik iraḥ, maca kuř ijj i x d ac ɣa iniɣ: ‘Wanita war kik ittriḥ!’, win war kik ittriḥ.”
\v 5 Issehwa řgens ɣar waman. \add Xenni\add* inna as SIDI: “Kuř ijj wenni i ɣa iřesḥen aman s yiřes nnes, am mammec i \add ten\add* iřesseḥ weqzin, ad t tegged ɣar ijj n ṭṭarf. Ammu uřa d marra inni i ɣa yaḍaren x ifadden maḥend ad swen.”
\v 6 Řqedd n yinni iwyen \add aman\add* s ufus nsen ɣar uqemmum nsen maḥend ad řesḥen \add aman\add* s yiřes nsen, tuɣa aten di teřt-mya n yeryazen, maca marra inneɣni uḍaren x ifadden ḥima ad swen aman.
\v 7 \add Xas\add* uca inna SIDI i Jidɛun: “S \add ufus n\add* teřt-mya n yeryazen-a, inni iřesḥen \add aman\add* s yiřes nsen, ad kenniw ssnejmeɣ u Necc ad ggeɣ Midyan deg ufus nnec. Marra řgens \add nneɣni i iqqimen\add* ad uyuren, kuř ijj ɣar wemcan nnes.
\v 8 Nitni ksin řeɛweč n řgens d waccawen nsen n icarri deg ufus, \add umi\add* netta issekk marra iryazen n Israil, kuř ijj ɣar uqiḍun nnes. \add Maca\add* teřt-mya n yeryazen nni ijja i-ten \add ɣares\add*. Tuɣa řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Midyan swadday nnes di řewḍa n teɣzurt.
\v 9 Di ǧiřet nni temsar, aqa SIDI inna as: “Kkar bedd, hwa ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, maɣar Necc ggiɣ ac ten deg ufus nnec.
\v 10 Mařa cek aqa teggʷded \add ɛad\add* maḥend ad dd-tehwid, hwa-dd \add xenni\add* ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar ak-d Fura, amsexxar nnec.
\v 11 Ad tesřed min xef ssawařen, uca xenni ad ac immewc jjehd deg ifassen nnec ařami ɣa tzemɛed ad tehwid ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.” \add Xenni\add* ihwa netta ak-d Fura, amsexxar nnes, ařami \add iwḍen\add* ař zzat i terbiɛin isswejden i umenɣi ɣar ṭṭarf n řmargeḥ.
\v 12 Uca Midyan d Ɛamaliq d marra ayt n ccarq tuɣa ssun di řewḍa n teɣzurt am yijj n weyřaf n tmurɣi u iřeɣman nsen war zemmaren ad ttwaḥesben, tuɣa aten deg waṭṭas am yijdi ɣar tma n řebḥar. \x ◘ \xo 7:12 \xt Řqḍ. 6:3, 5, 33\x*
\v 13 \add Umi\add* yiweḍ Jidɛun \add din\add*, xzar, ijj n weryaz, tuɣa ittḥaja i umeddukkeř nnes ict n tarjit, inna: “Xzar, necc ɣari ict n tarjit uca ẓriɣ mammec ijj n weɣrum n imendi i iwḍan ɣar swadday iqnunni-dd ɣar daxeř n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Midyan uca yiweḍ ař aqiḍun uca iřqef i-t ařami iwḍa u idweř x uzeǧif. Aqa \add ammu i\add* iwḍa uqiḍun.”
\v 14 Yarra-dd \add xas\add* umeddukkeř nnes, inna: “Aya war ixs ad yini mɣir ssif n Jidɛun, mmis n Yuwac, aryaz zi Israil. AREBBI iwca Midyan d marra řmargeḥ n řɛeskar deg ufus nnes.”
\v 15 \add Umi\add* isřa Jidɛun tarjit-a d min texs ad tini, yuḍar uca \add xenni\add* iɛqeb ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Israil, inna: “Kkarem, SIDI igga řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Midyan deg ufus nwem.”
\v 16 Jidɛun ibḍa teřt-mya n yeryazen x třata n ibaṭayunen uca iwca kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add* ijj n uyicc n icarri deg ufus nnes d ijj n weqḍuḥ ixwan d ijj n uṣefḍaw deg weqḍuḥ.
\v 17 Netta inna asen: “Xzarem-dd ɣari uca ggem amenni. Xzar, mařa iwḍeɣ ɣar ṭṭarf n řmargeḥ, xenni ad teggem uřa d kenniw am mammec i ɣa ggeɣ necc.
\v 18 Xmi ɣa suḍeɣ necc deg uyicc n icarri uřa d marra inni ɣari iǧan, xenni ad tsuḍem uřa d kenniw deg waccawen n icarri ɣar marra iɣezdisen n řmargeḥ, ad tinim: ‘I SIDI u i Jidɛun!’”
\v 19 Uca Jidɛun d mya n yeryazen nni tuɣa ɣares, iwḍen-dd ɣar ṭṭarf n řmargeḥ n řɛeskar ɣar umezwaru n tɛessast n wezyen \add n ǧiřet\add*, umi ten tuɣa \add ɛad\add* ggur ad ssbedden iɛessasen, uca suḍen deg waccawen n icarri, uca nitni wtin, arẓin iqḍuḥen nni ɣarsen deg ufus nsen.
\v 20 Třata n ibaṭayunen suḍen deg waccawen n icarri uca arẓin iqḍuḥen u s ufus aẓeřmaḍ ṭṭfen iṣefḍawen u s ufus afusi accawen n icarri ḥima ad \add daysen\add* suḍen uca sɣuyen: “Ssif n SIDI d Jidɛun!”
\v 21 Qqimen bedden ɣar marra iɣezdisen n řmargeḥ kuř ijj deg wemcan nnes. \add Xenni\add* bdan ad aẓẓřen \add marra inni iǧan di\add* řmargeḥ, sɣuyen uca arewřen.
\v 22 \add Umi\add* suḍen teřt-mya n yeryazen deg waccawen n icarri, issekkar SIDI ssif n ijjen ḍidd i wenneɣni di marra řmargeḥ uca yarweř řɛeskar ař Bayt-Ciṭṭa, jjihet n Zarara ař tma n \add yeɣzar i iǧan ɣar\add* Abil-Maḥula ɣar Ṭabbat. \x ◘ \xo 7:22 \xt Izhd. 83:10\x*
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* řaɣan-dd x yeryazen n Israil, zi Naftali u zi Acir u zi marra Manassa uca ḍfaren nitni \add ayt n\add* Midyan.
\v 24 \add Ɛawed\add* issekk Jidɛun ireqqasen ɣar marra idurar n Ifrayim, inna: “Hwam, uyurem ɣar umsagar ak-d ayt n Midyan u tekksem as iɣezran ař Bayt-Bara uřa d L’Urdun.” Ttwařaɣan marra iryazen n Ifrayim uca nitni ṭṭfen iɣezran ař Bayt-Bara d L’Urdun.
\v 25 Nitni ḥebbsen tnayen n řḥukkam n Midyan, Ɣurab d Di’ab, uca nɣin Ɣurab x teṣḍart n Ɣurab u Di’ab nɣin t x tsirt \add n uḍiř\add* n Di’ab uca nitni ɛerfen x Imidyaniyyen. Izeǧifen n Ɣurab d Di’ab iwyen ten ɣar Jidɛun x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun. \x ◘ \xo 7:25 \xt Izhd. 83:12; Ica. 10:26\x*
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Aɣelleb n Jidɛun x Midyan
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* nnan as yeryazen n Ifrayim: “Manawya i d aneɣ da teggid, aqa cek war i d xaneɣ třiɣid umi teffɣed, ḥima ad temmenɣed ak-d Midyan?” Uca nitni mmcubbecen akides aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt Řqḍ. 12:1\x*
\v 2 \add Jidɛun\add* yarra-dd xasen: “Mani i dd ɣa yas min ggiɣ ak-d min teggim? Ma war iǧi ařqaḍ n min iyuran n uḍiř n ayt n Ifrayim xar zi řɣiǧet n binu n ayt n Abiɛazar? \f ◼ \fr 8:2 \fk Jidɛun\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘netta’.\f*
\v 3 SIDI igga Ɣurab d Di’ab, řḥukkam n Midyan, deg ufus nwem. Min zemmareɣ ad ggeɣ ad t ssemquddeɣ akidwem?” Umi netta inna awař-a yarsa uxeyyeq nsen.
\b
\m 
\v 4 \add Umi\add* dd-yusa Jidɛun ɣar L’Urdun, iẓwa netta ak-d teřt-mya n yeryazen nni tuɣa ɣares iǧan. Nitni fnan řami ten qqimen ḍeffaren \add ayt n Midyan\add*.
\v 5 Inna netta i yeryazen n Sukkut: “Ttzawgeɣ, wcem i řgens i dd ayi iḍfaren x iḍaren ticnifin n weɣrum, maɣar nitni fnan u necc aqa ḍeffareɣ Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ, ijeǧiden n Midyan.”
\v 6 \add Maca\add* řḥukkam n Sukkut nnan: “Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ, ma aqa aten deg ufus nnec, maḥend ad newc aɣrum i řɛeskar nnec?”
\v 7 S uya inna Jidɛun: “Xenni řexxu, xmi d ayi ɣa igg SIDI Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ deg ufus inu, \add xenni\add* ad awem ssarewteɣ aysum n arrimet nwem ak-d isennanen d yeẓra n tmessi zi řexřa.”
\v 8 Uca igeɛɛed ssenni ɣar Fanuwil uca issiweř amenni akidsen. Arrin-dd xas yeryazen n Fanuwil am mammec i dd-arrin yeryazen n Sukkut.
\v 9 S uyenni issiweř ɛawed ak-d yeryazen n Fanuwil, inna: “Mařa necc ɛeqbeɣ-dd di řehna, ad hedmeɣ ṣṣumɛet-a ta.”
\m 
\v 10 \add Tuɣa\add* Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ ak-d řɛeskar nsen di Karkur, tuɣa aten ɛřaḥař di xemmesṭac-ařef n yeryazen, marra inni tuɣa iqqimen zi marra řɛeskar n ayt n ccarq. Aqa mya u-ɛicrin-ařef n yeryazen inni izemmaren x ssif tuɣa ttwanɣen \add ɛad\add*.
\v 11 Uca igeɛɛed Jidɛun ak-d webrid n yinni izeddɣen deg iqiḍan, ɣar ccarq n Nubaḥ d Yujbaha u netta iɣřeb x řɛeskar nni, umi \add iɛeskariyyen di\add* řmargeḥ \add ittɣiř asen\add* aqa aten di řaman.
\v 12 Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ arewřen uca netta iḍfar i-ten. Iṭṭef tnayen n ijeǧiden n Midyan, Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ, d imeḥbas uca issiggʷed marra řɛeskar. \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt Izhd.83:12\x*
\m 
\v 13 \add Umi\add* dd-iɛqeb Jidɛun, mmis n Yuwac, zeg umenɣi, ikka x tsunta n Ḥaras,
\v 14 iṭṭef ijj n webřiɣ zeg yeryazen n Sukkut d ameḥbus uca isseqsa t. Wanita yura as \add marra ismawen n\add* řḥukkam n Sukkut d imɣaren nsen, sebɛa u-sebɛin n yeryazen.
\v 15 \add Umi\add* dd-yiweḍ netta ɣar yeryazen n Sukkut, inna: “Ina d Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ, inni zi i d ayi tessbarrqem umi tennam: ‘Ma Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ aqa aten deg ufus nnec ař ɣa newc aɣrum i yeryazen nnec nni yuḥřen?’”
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* iṭṭef imɣaren n tendint d isennanen d iẓra n tmessi zi řexřa uca igga iryazen n Sukkut ad zzayes acan.
\v 17 Lburj n Fanuwil ihdem i-t u inɣa iryazen n tendint.
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* inna i Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ: “Mammec iǧan yeryazen nni tenɣim di Tabur?” Nitni arrin-dd xas: “Nitni tuɣa aten am cek, \add ɣarsen\add* addud d ijjen \add ak-d\add* iḥenjiren n ujeǧid.”
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* inna: “Nitni tuɣa d aytma, iḥenjiren n yemma. S tidett am iddar SIDI, mři ten tejjim ad ddaren, iři war kenniw neqqeɣ!”
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* inna i Yatar, amenzu nnes: “Kkar, neɣ i-ten!” \add Maca\add* abřiɣ war dd-ikkis ssif nnes, minzi netta iggʷed umi ɛad d abřiɣ.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* nnan Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ: “Kkar cek simant nnec uca neɣ aneɣ, maɣar mammec aryaz, ammu tizemmar nnes.” Uca ikkar Jidɛun, inɣa Zabaḥ d Ṣalmunnaɛ uca iksi tiziriwin timeẓyanin i d yuyřen ɣar irawen n iřeɣman nsen. \x ◘ \xo 8:21 \xt Izhd. 83:12\x*
\b
\s1 Aɛbed n l’aṣnam zi Jidɛun d řmewt nnes
\m 
\v 22 Uca iryazen n Israil nnan i Jidɛun: “Ḥekmet xaneɣ, cek uřa d mmic d wayyaw nnec, maɣar cek tfekked aneɣ zeg ufus n Midyan.”
\v 23 Inna asen Jidɛun: “\bd Necc\bd* war xawem ḥekkmeɣ uřa d mmi war xawem iḥekkem. SIDI d wenni i xawem i ɣa iḥekmen.”
\v 24 Jidɛun yarni inna asen: “Necc xseɣ ad zzaywem ttareɣ ca. Ad ayi iwc kuř ijj n weryaz ict n texrazt zi tkeccaḍt nnes!”, minzi \add ttwafen\add* ɣarsen texrazin n wureɣ, maɣar nitni tuɣa aten d ayt n Ismaɛil.
\v 25 Nitni nnan: “Neccin ad ac tent newc s řxaḍar!” Nitni bezzɛen ijj n werruḍ uca kuř aryaz inḍar xas ict n texrazt zi tkeccaḍt nnes.
\v 26 Tixrazin n wureɣ nni ittar weznent sbeɛṭac-mya n \add ciqlu\add* wureɣ, nhřa tiziriwin timeẓyanin d texrazin di ṣṣifet n tuddimin d werruḍ arjuwani i tuɣa yarḍen ijeǧiden n Midyan, nhřa tiseddyin \add i yuyřen\add* ɣar irawen n iřeɣman nsen.
\v 27 Jidɛun igga zzayes ijj n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* uca igga i-t di tendint nnes, di Ɛafra, u marra Israil yuyur awarni as am awarni i yict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř. Aya idweř d řfex i Jidɛun d taddart nnes.
\v 28 \add Ammu\add* tuɣa innbehdeř Midyan zeg ayt n Israil uca war zemmaren ad ssgeɛɛden azeǧif nsen ɛad. Tuɣa tammurt tareyyeḥ arebɛin n iseggʷusa deg wussan n Jidɛun.
\m 
\v 29 Uca Yarubbaɛl, mmis n Yuwac, yuyur uca izdeɣ \add ɛawed\add* di taddart nnes.
\v 30 Jidɛun tuɣa ɣares sebɛin n iḥenjiren inni dd-iffɣen zi tmeṣṣaḍt nnes, minzi tuɣa ɣares aṭṭas n temɣarin.
\v 31 Uřa d tayya nnes tenni \add tuɣa iǧan\add* di Cakim, tejja as-dd ijj n uḥenjir u netta igga as Abimalik.
\v 32 Jidɛun, mmis n Yuwac, immut \add umi\add* acuwwaf nnes \add tuɣa\add* icab aṭṭas uca nḍřen t deg wenḍeř n babas Yuwac, di Ɛafra, \add tandint\add* n Abiɛazari.
\m 
\v 33 \add Awarni řami\add* immut Jidɛun, imsar, aqa ayt n Israil dewřen-dd uca ssfesden ixef nsen am uyuren awarni i ‘Ibaɛlen’ uca ggin Baɛl-Barit d arebbi nsen.
\v 34 Ayt n Israil war fekkaren ɛad di SIDI, AREBBI nsen, wenni ten ifekken zeg ufus n marra řɛedyan i d asen dd-innḍen
\v 35 uca war ssecnen tamexsiwt icewwaren i taddart n Yarubbaɛl, d tenni n Jidɛun, x marra řxar i igga di ṭṭweɛ n Israil.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Abimalik d imezdaɣ n Cakim
\m 
\v 1 Abimalik, mmis n Yarubbaɛl, yuyur ɣar Cakim, ɣar aytmas n yemmas. Netta issiweř akidsen u ak-d marra řwacun n taddart n babas n yemmas, inna:
\v 2 “Siwřem maca deg imezzuɣen n marra imezdaɣ n Cakim: ‘Min iǧan mliḥ i kenniw: mařa sebɛin n yeryazen ad xawem ḥekmen, marra iḥenjiren n Yarubbaɛl, niɣ mařa mɣir ijj n weryaz waha ad xawem iḥkem? Ɛeqřem ɛawed, aqa necc d iɣussan nwem d aysum nwem.’”
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* ssiwřen aytmas n yemmas marra awařen-a deg imezzuɣen n marra imezdaɣ n Cakim ařami uř nsen imeyyeř ad dd-yas ak-d Abimalik, maɣar nitni nnan: “Netta d umatneɣ.”
\v 4 Nitni wcin as sebɛin n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart zi zzawect n Baɛl-Barit. Zzaysent icra Abimalik iryazen ixwan d yinni iṭarrcen, uca nitni ḍeffaren t-i-dd.
\v 5 Yudef ɣar taddart n babas di Ɛafra u inɣa x ijj n weẓru aytmas, iḥenjiren n Yarubbaɛl, sebɛin n yeryazen. Mɣir Yutam, aḥenjir amaẓuẓ n Yarubbaɛl iqqim weḥḥdes, minzi netta tuɣa innuffar. \f ◼ \fr 9:5 \fk Yutam\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘Arebbi d wenni ikemřen’ niɣ ‘Arebbi břa řɛib’.\f*
\v 6 Uca munen marra imezdaɣ n Cakim d marra inni di lqelɛa uca ffɣen, ggin Abimalik d ajeǧid ɣar tcejjart n yigg nni \add iǧan\add* deg wemcan \add iqeddsen\add* ɣar Cakim. \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt Yac. 24:26\x*
\v 7 Nitni xebbaren aya i Yutam, ikkar ibedd x tqiccat n wedrar n Jarizim. Issgeɛɛed tmijja nnes, inna asen: “Sřem ɣari, \add a kenniw\add* imezdaɣ n Cakim, uca AREBBI ad ɣarwem iseř!”
\b
\m 
\v 8 “Acḥař uya kkarent tcejjura, ffɣent ḥima ad dehnent ijj n ujeǧid x yixef nsent uca nnant i uzemmur: ‘Iři cek d ajeǧid nneɣ!’
\v 9 Azemmur inna asen: ‘Ma ad semḥeɣ di tadunt \add n zzect\add* inu nni i d ayi issemɣar AREBBI d iwdan? Ma ad ḍweɣ sennej i tcejjura nneɣni?’
\m 
\v 10 Uca nnant tcejjura i wartu: ‘As-dd, iři cek d ajeǧid nneɣ!’
\v 11 Urtu inna asen: ‘Ma ad semḥeɣ di taẓyudi inu d řɣiǧet iṣebḥen inu? Ma ad ḍweɣ sennej i tcejjura nneɣni?’
\m 
\v 12 Uca nnant tcejjura i tzayart: ‘As-dd, iři cem d ajeǧid nneɣ!’
\v 13 \add Maca\add* tenna asen tzayart: ‘Ma ad semḥeɣ di binu n jdid inu nni issefraḥen AREBBI d iwdan? Ma ad ḍweɣ sennej i tcejjura nneɣni?’
\m 
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* nnan marra ticejjura i cbarq ak-d isennanen: ‘As-dd, iři cek d ajeǧid nneɣ!’
\v 15 Uca cbarq ak-d isennanen inna i tcejjura: ‘Mařa texsent kennint s tidett ad ayi tdehnent d ajeǧid xakent, asent-dd xenni, afent adurri di tiři inu, maca mařa lla, \add xenni\add* ad tekkar tmessi zi cbarq ak-d isennanen, ad tecc \add ticejjura n\add* tengelt n Lubnan.’”
\b
\m 
\v 16 Řexxu xenni, kenniw, \add imezdaɣ n Cakim\add*, mařa teggim s tidett d řeṣfayet \add umi\add* teggim Abimalik d ajeǧid, u mařa kenniw teggim mliḥ di Yarubbaɛl d taddart nnes, u mařa kenniw teggim dayes am mammec issdaheǧ,
\v 17 - aqa baba immneɣ di ṭṭweɛ nwem uca isebbeř tudart nnes uca ifekk kenniw zeg ufus n Midyan,
\v 18 \add maca\add* kenniw tɣewwɣem ass-a x taddart n baba u x ijj n weẓru aqa tenɣim arraw nnes, sebɛin n yeryazen, u teggim Abimalik, mmis n tayya, d ajeǧid x imezdaɣ n Cakim, minzi netta d umatwem -
\v 19 mařa kenniw teggim ass-a s tidett d řeṣfayet di Yarubbaɛl d taddart nnes, xenni ad tfarḥem di Abimalik u netta ad ifarḥ daywem.
\v 20 Maca mařa war iǧi amenni, \add xenni\add* ad tekkar tmessi zi Abimalik ad tecc iryazen n Cakim d imezdaɣ n lqelɛa uca ad tekkar tmessi zeg imezdaɣ n Cakim u zi marra inni di lqelɛa, ad tecc Abimalik!’”
\m 
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* yuyur Yutam, yarweř, iruḥ ɣar Bi’r. Tuɣa izeddeɣ din, \add iggʷej\add* x umas Abimalik. \f ◼ \fr 9:21 \fk x umas\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘x wudem n umas’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 22 \add Řami\add* tuɣa iḥekkem Abimalik x Israil třata n iseggʷusa,
\v 23 issekk AREBBI ijj n řaryaḥ d aɛeffan jar Abimalik d imezdaɣ n Cakim. Imezdaɣ n Cakim ɣdaren zi Abimalik,
\v 24 ḥima aɣeṣṣeb, \add nni ittwaggen i\add* sebɛin n iḥenjiren n Yarubbaɛl, d idammen nsen ad dd-asen x umatsen Abimalik, wenni ten inɣin, u x imezdaɣ n Cakim, inni tuɣa issjehden ifassen nnes maḥend ad nɣen aytmas.
\v 25 Imezdaɣ n Cakim wejden as řefxux x tqiccat n idurar u nitni keccḍen marra wenni din xasen i ɣa ikken d abrid. Aya ittwanna i Abimalik.
\v 26 Jaɛal, mmis n Ɛabid, yusa-dd ak-d aytmas uca nitni uyuren ɣar Cakim u imezdaɣ n Cakim ttiqqen dayes.
\v 27 Nitni ffɣen ɣar iyyaren, řeqḍen uḍiř deg imarjaɛen nsen, ɛeffsen x uḍiř uca ɣennjen izřan n řefraḥet, udfen ɣar taddart n arebbi nsen, ccin swin uca neɛřen Abimalik.
\v 28 Uca Jaɛal, mmis n Ɛabid, inna: “Min \add iɛna netta\add* Abimalik d man wen \add i iǧan\add* d Cakim, aqa neccin ad as naḍar? Ma war iǧi netta d mmis n Yarubbaɛl? U ma war iǧi Zabul d lwali nnes? Sexxarem \add xenni\add* i yeryazen n Ḥamur, babas n Cakim, minzi mayemmi i d as ɣa nsexxar?
\v 29 Mři maca řgens-a deg ufus inu, \add xenni\add* necc tuɣa xseɣ ad aẓẓřeɣ x Abimalik.” Uca inna i Abimalik: “Arni i řɛeskar nnec uca ffeɣ \add ɣar umenɣi\add*!”
\m 
\v 30 \add Umi\add* Zabul, řḥakem n tendint, isřa awařen n Jaɛal, mmis n Ɛabid, yarɣa uxeyyeq nnes.
\v 31 Netta issekk ireqqasen ɣar Abimalik di tnuffra, nnan: “Xzar, Jaɛal, mmis n Ɛabid, d aytmas usin-dd ɣar Cakim, u xzar, aqa ssɣewwɣen xak tandint.
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, kkar di ǧiřet-a, cek d řgens nni ɣarek iǧan, uca egg ijj n řfex deg iyyar.
\v 33 U ɣar tuffut, ɣar wenqar n tfuct, ittxeṣṣa ad tekkared zic uca ɛref x tendint. U xzar, mařa netta d řgens i ɣares ad ɣarek dd-iffeɣ, egg xenni akides min xef izemmar ufus nnec ad igg.”
\v 34 Abimalik d marra řgens i ɣares, ikkar-dd di ǧiřet u nitni ggin ijj n řfex x Cakim s arebɛa n ibaṭayunen.
\m 
\v 35 U Jaɛal, mmis n Ɛabid, iffeɣ-dd, yuyur ɣar tewwart n tendint u Abimalik, d marra řgens i ɣares, ikkar zeg wemcan innuffaren.
\v 36 \add Umi\add* Jaɛal iẓra řgens, inna i Zabul: “Xzar, aqa iwdan hekkwan-dd zi tqiccat n idurar.” Zabul inna as: “Cek twařid tiři n idurar d iwdan.”
\v 37 Jaɛal yarni issawař, inna: “Xzar, aqa \add ijj n ubarru\add* n řgens ihekkwa-dd zi tɛebbuḍt n temmurt u ict n řkumpaniyyet tusa-dd zeg webrid n tcejjart n yigg n ibezgawen.”
\v 38 Xenni inna as Zabul: “Mani i ǧan řexxu wawařen nnec i zi tennid: ‘Min \add iɛna\add* Abimalik, aqa neccin ad as nsexxar? Ma war ǧin ina d řgens i tesseḥqared cek? Ffeɣ \add xenni\add* řexxu u temmenɣed akides!”
\v 39 Uca iffeɣ Jaɛal zzat i wudem n imezdaɣ n Cakim uca immneɣ ak-d Abimalik.
\v 40 Iḍfar i-t Abimalik, minzi netta yarweř zzat i wudem nnes uca aṭṭas n yinni ittwassnuqqben \add s ssif\add* wḍan ař adaf n tewwart n tendint.
\v 41 Iqqim Abimalik di Aruma u Zabul yuẓẓeř x Jaɛal d aytmas ařami war zemmaren ad qqimen ɛad di Cakim.
\m 
\v 42 Tiwecca nnes, imsar, řgens iffeɣ ɣar iyyar. Aya ɛawden t i Abimalik.
\v 43 \add Xenni\add* iksi netta řgens, ibḍa t x třata n ibaṭayunen uca igga ijj n řfex deg iyyar uca netta ixezzar, aqa řgens iffeɣ zi tendint. \add Xenni\add* ikkar ḍidd nsen uca iɣřeb xasen.
\v 44 \add Minzi\add* Abimalik d ibaṭayunen i ɣares, ffɣen uca uyuren ad bedden ɣar tewwart n tendint, u tnayen n ibaṭayunen nneɣnit udfen x yinni \add tuɣa\add* deg iyyar uca qḍan xasen.
\v 45 Ass nni marra immneɣ Abimalik ak-d tendint. Netta iṭṭef i-tt, inɣa řgens i dayes \add iǧan\add*. \add Xenni\add* ihdem tandint uca issuyes xas tameǧaḥt.
\m 
\v 46 \add Umi\add* t sřin marra imezdaɣ n lburj, udfen ɣar amcan n warwař n taddart n arebbi \add nsen\add* Barit. \f ◼ \fr 9:46 \fk Barit\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘řɛahd’. S uyenni ‘arebbi n řɛahd’.\f*
\v 47 Ittwanna i Abimalik, aqa marra imezdaɣ n lburj n Cakim ggin ad munen \add din\add*.
\v 48 \add Xas\add* uca igeɛɛed Abimalik adrar n Ṣalmun, netta ak-d marra řgens i ɣares \add iǧan\add*, u Abimalik iṭṭef ccaqur nnes deg ufus uca iqřeɛ ict n tṣeṭṭa n tcejjart, iksi tt u issars i-tt x teɣruḍt nnes, inna i řgens nnes: “Min teẓrim ggiɣ necc, qeǧqem, ggem \add t\add* uřa d kenniw am necc!”
\v 49 U marra řgens, kuř aryaz, iqřeɛ taṣeṭṭa nnes uca ḍfaren Abimalik u ssarsen tent ɣar wemcan n warwař uca qqedmen asen timessi x wemcan n warwař ařami mmuten uřa d marra iryazen n lburj n Cakim, ɛřaḥař ařef n yeryazen d temɣarin.
\m 
\v 50 Iruḥ Abimalik \add ɛawed\add* ɣar Tabaṣ, iwta iqiḍan nnes ɣar Tabaṣ uca iṭṭef i-tt.
\v 51 Tuɣa di řwesṭ n tendint ijj n lburj imettnen u arewřen ɣares marra iryazen d temɣarin d marra imezdaɣ n tendint uca nitni bellɛen xasen, nyin x tzeqqa n lburj.
\v 52 Yiweḍ Abimalik ɣar lburj u immneɣ akides, \add maca\add* xmi netta dd-iqarreb ɣar tewwart n lburj ḥima ad as iqqed timessi,
\v 53 tenḍar ict n temɣart ict n taṣḍart n tsirt yuɛřan x uzeǧif n Abimalik uca teřbez as aceqquf \add n uzeǧif\add*. \x ◘ \xo 9:53 \xt 2 Ṣm. 11:21\x*
\v 54 Deɣya iřaɣa netta i umsexxar \add nnes\add* wenni d as yarebbun řesnaḥ, inna as: “Jbedd ssif nnec uca neɣ ayi, ḥima war xafi qqaren: ‘Ict temɣart tenɣa i-t’.” Uca aḥudri nnes issnuqqeb i-t uca immut.
\v 55 \add Umi\add* ẓrin iryazen n Israil, aqa Abimalik immut, ffɣen-dd, \add kuř ijj n\add* weryaz ɣar wemcan \add n tzeddiɣt\add* nnes.
\m 
\v 56 \add Ammu\add* i ixeǧeṣ AREBBI tuɛeffna n Abimalik nni igga i babas umi inɣa sebɛin n aytmas.
\v 57 Marra tuɛeffna i iggin iryazen n Cakim yarr i-tt AREBBI x uzeǧif nsen u nneɛřet n Yutam, mmis n Yarubbaɛl, tewḍa-dd xasen.
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Tulaɛ, Ya’ir d Yaftaḥ
\m 
\v 1 Awarni Abimalik ikkar \bd Tulaɛ\bd*, mmis n Fuwa, mmis n Dudu, ijj n weryaz zi \add teqbič n\add* Issakar, ḥima ad issenjem Israil. Netta tuɣa izeddeɣ di Camir x idurar n Ifrayim.
\v 2 Netta tuɣa d řqaḍi x Israil třata u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa. \add Xenni\add* immut, ittwanḍeř di Camir.
\m 
\v 3 Awarni as ikkar \bd Ya’ir\bd*, Ajilɛadi. Netta tuɣa d řqaḍi x Israil tnayen u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa.
\v 4 Netta tuɣa ɣares třatin n iḥenjiren, inni innayen x třatin n iɣyař u ɣarsen třatin n tneddam, ttřaɣan asent ‘dcurat n Ya’ir’ ař ass-a. Aqa atent di temmurt n Jilɛad.
\v 5 Uca immut Ya’ir, neḍřen t di Qamun.
\b
\m 
\v 6 Ayt n Israil arnin ad ggen min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Nitni sexxaren i ‘Ibaɛlen’ d ‘Ɛactarutin’ uřa d irebbiten n Aram d irebbiten n Ṣidun d irebbiten n Mu’ab d irebbiten n Ɛammun d irebbiten n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Nitni jjin SIDI u war d as sexxaren \add ɛad\add*. \x ◘ \xo 10:6 \xt Řqḍ. 2:11; 3:7; 4:1; 6:1\x*
\v 7 Yarɣa weɣḍab n SIDI x i Israil u Netta igga i-ten deg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen u deg ufus n ayt n Ɛammun.
\v 8 Deg useggʷas nni řebzen u arẓin nitni ayt n Israil. \add Ammu i iggin nitni\add* tmenṭac n iseggʷusa ak-d ayt n Israil inni \add iǧan\add* x ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun, di temmurt n Imuriy\add yen\add*, tenni di Jilɛad.
\v 9 Uca \add ɛawed\add* ẓwan ayt n Ɛammun L’Urdun ḥima ad mmenɣen uřa ak-d Yahuda d Binyamin d taddart n Ifrayim \add ařami\add* ittwaḥsar Israil aṭṭas.
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* sɣuyen ayt n Israil ɣar SIDI, nnan: “Neccin nexḍa akidek, minzi neccin nesmeḥ di AREBBI nneɣ, nsexxar ‘Ibaɛlen’.”
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna SIDI i ayt n Israil: “Ma war \add kenniw ssnejmeɣ\add* zeg \add ufus n\add* Imiṣriyyen d Imuriyyen u zeg \add ufus n\add* ayt n Ɛammun d Ifilisṭiniyyen
\v 12 u zeg \add ufus n ayt n\add* Ṣidun u zeg \add ufus n\add* ayt n Ɛamaliq d Imaɛuniyyen, inni tuɣa kenniw iḥṣaren umi kenniw i d ɣari tesɣuyem, ma \add xenni\add* Necc war ssnejmeɣ kenniw zeg ufus nsen?
\v 13 \add Waxxa amenni\add* kenniw tsemḥem dayi u tsexxarem i irebbiten nneɣni. S uya war kenniw ssenjimeɣ ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 10:13 \xt Aɛwd. 32:15; Irm. 2:13\x*
\v 14 Uyurem, tesɣuyem ɣar irebbiten nni tareccḥem i yixef nwem. Jjem ten ad kenniw ssnejmen di řweqt n řeḥṣaret nwem.”
\v 15 \add Maca\add* ayt n Israil nnan i SIDI: “Neccin aqa nexḍa. Egg \bd Cek\bd* akidneɣ marra min i d ac iɛejben di tiṭṭawin nnec, mɣir fekk aneɣ ass-a waha!”
\v 16 U nitni ssiggʷejen irebbiten iɣriben zi řwesṭ nsen uca sexxaren i SIDI. \add Xenni\add* war izemmar řeɛmar nnes ad tarbu \add ɛad\add* řeɣben n Israil.
\v 17 Ttwasmunen ayt n Ɛammun uca wtin iqiḍan nsen di Jilɛad. Uřa d ayt n Israil munen u nitni wtin iqiḍan nsen di Miṣfa.
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* inna řgens, řḥukkam n Jilɛad, i wayawya: “Man aryaz i ɣa immenɣen d amezwaru ak-d ayt n Ɛammun? Netta ad idweř d azeǧif x marra imezdaɣ n Jilɛad.” \x ◘ \xo 10:18 \xt Řqḍ. 11:6, 9, 10, 11\x*
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Yaftaḥ d ayt n Ɛammun
\m 
\v 1 \bd Yaftaḥ\bd*, zi \add temmurt n\add* Jilɛad, tuɣa-t d ijj n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen, \add maca\add* netta \add tuɣa\add* d mmis n ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř. Jilɛad aqa ijja-dd Yaftaḥ \add ɣares\add*. \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt Ɛbr. 11:32\x*
\v 2 Uřa d tamɣart n Jilɛad turuw as-dd iḥenjiren. \add Umi\add* iḥenjiren n temɣart-a mɣaren, uẓẓřen x Yaftaḥ, nnan as: “Cek war tᵉttᵉṭṭifed ca tasɣart di taddart n babatneɣ, maɣar cek d mmis n ict n temɣart nneɣnit.”
\v 3 Uca yarweř Yaftaḥ zeg wudem n aytmas u netta iqqim izdeɣ di temmurt n Ṭub. Uca ict n tewrawt n yeryazen xwan usin-dd ɣar Yaftaḥ, ffɣen-dd akides.
\v 4 Awarni \add aṭṭas n\add* wussan imsar, kkaren ayt n Ɛammun mmenɣen ak-d Israil.
\v 5 Uca imsar, umi ayt n Ɛammun mmenɣen ak-d Israil, aqa imɣaren n Jilɛad ṭṭfen abrid ḥima ad awyen Yaftaḥ zi temmurt n Ṭub.
\v 6 Nitni nnan i Yaftaḥ: “As-dd, iři d akumandar nneɣ u ejj aneɣ ad nemmneɣ ak-d ayt n Ɛammun.”
\v 7 Yaftaḥ inna i imɣaren n Jilɛad: “Ma war d ayi tɛiffem u tuẓẓřem xafi zi taddart n baba? Mayemmi i dd ɣari tusim řexxu, \add řexxu\add* umi teǧam di řeḥṣaret?”
\v 8 Arrin-dd imɣaren n Jilɛad x Yaftaḥ: “S uya i dd ɣarek nusa řexxu, \add ḥima\add* cek akidneɣ tuyured ad temmenɣed ak-d ayt n Ɛammun. Cek ad ɣarneɣ tiřid d azeǧif x marra imezdaɣ n Jilɛad.”
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna Yaftaḥ i imɣaren n Jilɛad: “Mařa kenniw tarrim ayi ɣar umenɣi ak-d ayt n Ɛammun u SIDI isellem i-ten zzat i wudem inu, ad dewřeɣ d azeǧif nwem!”
\v 10 Imɣaren n Jilɛad nnan i Yaftaḥ: “Ad yiři SIDI d wenni ittesřan jar aneɣ. \add Uct xaneɣ\add* mařa war nᵉttegg ɛlaḥsab awařen nnec.”
\v 11 Xas uca yuyur Yaftaḥ ak-d imɣaren n Jilɛad u řgens igga i-t d azeǧif d akumandar x yixef nnes. Uca issiweř Yaftaḥ marra awařen nnes zzat i wudem n SIDI di Miṣfa.
\v 12 Uca issekk Yaftaḥ ireqqasen ɣar ujeǧid n ayt n Ɛammun, inna: “Min din jar ayi d cek, aqa cek teffɣed, ḥima ad temmenɣed ḍidd i temmurt inu?”
\v 13 Inna ujeǧid n ayt n Ɛammun i ireqqasen n Yaftaḥ: “Minzi Israil tuɣa iṭṭef tammurt inu zeg Arnun ař Yabbuq u ař L’Urdun, umi dd-iffeɣ zi Miṣra. Arr ayi-tt řexxu s řehna!”
\v 14 Issekk Yaftaḥ ɛawed ireqqasen ɣar ujeǧid n ayt n Ɛammun.
\v 15 Inna as: “Ammu i iqqar Yaftaḥ: ‘Israil war iṭṭif ca tammurt n Mu’ab d temmurt n ayt n Ɛammun, \x ◘ \xo 11:15 \xt Řxř. 21:13; Aɛwd. 2:9, 19\x*
\v 16 minzi umi dd-ffɣen zi Miṣra, yuyur Israil di řexřa ař Řebḥar n Telga uca \add ɣar uneggar\add* yusa-dd ɣar Qadac.
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* issekk Israil ireqqasen ɣar ujeǧid n Idum, inna: ‘Ejj ayi ad cuqeɣ di temmurt nnec!’ Maca ajeǧid n Idum war isři ca. Issekk ɛawed \add ireqqasen\add* ɣar ujeǧid n Mu’ab uca uřa d netta war iwc ttesriḥ. \add Ammu\add* iqqim Israil di Qadac. \x ◘ \xo 11:17 \xt Řxř. 20:17\x*
\v 18 Uca yuyur \add řgens\add* di řexřa, inneḍ i temmurt n Idum d temmurt n Mu’ab uca yusa-dd \add ammu\add* ɣar uɣezdis n temmurt n Mu’ab \add i iǧan\add* ɣar mani tneqqar tfuct uca nitni wtin iqiḍan nsen aɣirin i Arnun, maca war dd-usin daxeř i weymir \add n temmurt\add* n Mu’ab, maɣar Arnun d aymir n Mu’ab.
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* issekk Israil ireqqasen ɣar Siḥun, ajeǧid n Imuriyyen, ajeǧid n Ḥacbun, uca inna as Israil: ‘Ejj aneɣ ad ncuq tammurt nnec ař amcan \add i ɣar i ɣa uyureɣ\add*.’ \x ◘ \xo 11:19 \xt Řxř. 21:22; Aɛwd. 2:26\x*
\v 20 \add Maca\add* Siḥun war ittiqq Israil ař i ɣa icuq tammurt nnes \add waha\add*. U Siḥun issmun marra řgens nnes uca nitni wtin iqiḍan nsen di Jahaṣ. Uca \add xenni\add* immneɣ netta ak-d Israil.
\v 21 SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, igga \add xenni\add* Siḥun d marra řgens nnes deg ufus n Israil uca ɣeřben xasen. Marra tammurt n Imuriy\add yen\add*, inni tuɣa izeddɣen di temmurt nni, iṭṭef i-tt Israil d řwart.
\v 22 Nitni ṭṭfen marra tammurt n Imuriy\add yen\add* d tasɣart, zeg Arnun ař Yabbuq u zi řexřa ař L’Urdun. \x ◘ \xo 11:22 \xt Aɛwd. 2:36\x*
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, aqa yuẓẓeř SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, x Imuriy\add yen\add* zzat i wudem n řgens n Israil zi řwart nsen u ma cek \add xenni\add* ad tt tᵉṭṭfed d tasɣart?
\v 24 Ma war tᵉṭṭifed ca d tasɣart min d ac ɣa iwc arebbi nnec Kamuc d řwart? \add Ammu\add* i ɣa neṭṭef marra d řwart min d aneɣ ɣa iwc SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, d řwart.
\v 25 Xenni řexxu, ma cek xar s waṭṭas x Balak, mmis n Ṣiffur, ajeǧid n Mu’ab? Ma netta \add ɛemmarṣ ma\add* imcubbec ak-d Israil? Ma \add ɛemmarṣ ma\add* immneɣ akidsen? \x ◘ \xo 11:25 \xt Řxř. 22:2\x*
\v 26 Israil tuɣa izdeɣ ɛad teřt-mya n iseggʷusa di Ḥacbun u di tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen u di Ɛaruɛir d tneddam i ɣares dd-iqqnen u di marra tineddam nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar tmuwwa n Arnun. Mayemmi war tent tfekkem \add xenni\add* di marra řweqt nni?
\v 27 \bd Necc\bd* war kik xḍiɣ, \add maca\add* cek tegged ayi řɣar umi akidi temmenɣed. SIDI, wenni d Řqaḍi, ad iḥkem ass-a jar ayt n Israil u jar ayt n Ɛammun!”
\v 28 \add Maca\add* ajeǧid n ayt n Ɛammun war isři ɣar wawařen nni d as dd-issekk Yaftaḥ \add s ufus n ijj n ureqqas\add*.
\v 29 Uca ihwa-dd Arruḥ n SIDI x Yaftaḥ u netta iẓwa Jilɛad d Manassa. Netta iẓwa \add ɛawed\add* x Miṣfa di Jilɛad uca iẓwa \add xenni\add* ɣar ayt n Ɛammun.
\v 30 Uca iwaɛd Yaftaḥ ijj n lwaɛd i SIDI, inna: “Mařa Cek ad tegged ayt n Ɛammun qaɛ deg ufus inu,
\v 31 \add xenni\add*, mařa ɛeqbeɣ-dd di řehna zeg ayt n Ɛammun, min i dd ɣa iffɣen zi tewwura n taddart inu ḥima ad kidi immeřqa, ad yiři i SIDI u necc ad as t qeddmeɣ d tasɣart n wecmaḍ.”
\m 
\v 32 \add Xas uca\add* iẓwa Yaftaḥ ɣar ayt n Ɛammun ḥima ad kisen immneɣ uca SIDI igga i-ten deg ufus nnes.
\v 33 Netta iɣřeb xasen zi Ɛaruɛir ař mani tiwḍed ɣar Minnit, ɛicrin n tneddam, ař Abal-Kurum, aqa-tt d ict n tecti d tameqqrant aṭṭas. \add Ammu\add* i dd-ttwassehwan ayt n Ɛammun zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil. \f ◼ \fr 11:33 \fk Abal-Kurum\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘řewḍa n (iḥwicen n) tzayarin’.\f*
\m 
\v 34 Umi dd-yusa Yaftaḥ ɣar Miṣfa ɣar taddart nnes, xzar, teffeɣ-dd ɣares yeǧis ḥima ad t-i-dd teřqa barra s ibendiren d ccḍiḥ \add s nnubtat\add*. Nettat tuɣa d ayenni ɣares \add n yeǧis\add*, netta tuɣa war ɣares aḥenjir uřa d taḥenjirt nneɣnit.
\v 35 \add Umi\add* tt iẓra, icarreg arruḍ nnes, inna: “A wayyaw, yeǧi, cem tessehwid ayi-dd aṭṭas u tdewřed ɣar yinni i d ayi itteggen řeḥřiq minzi necc arzmeɣ aqemmum inu i SIDI, war zemmareɣ ad dd-dewřeɣ \add ɛad\add*.”
\v 36 Nettat tenna as: “Baba inu! \add Mařa\add* cek tarzmed aqemmum nnec i SIDI, \add xenni\add* egg kidi ɛlaḥsab \add awař\add* i dd-iffɣen zeg uqemmum nnec, maɣar intaqem SIDI qaɛ di ṭṭweɛ nnec x řɛedyan nnec, x ayt n Ɛammun.”
\v 37 U nettat tenna \add ɛawed\add* i babas: “Iři ad kidi ittwagg \add ɛlaḥsab\add* awař-a. Ejj ayi tnayen n iyuren, \add maḥend\add* necc ad uyureɣ, ad dd-hwiɣ \add maḥend\add* ad ruɣ x idurar x tuɛezriya inu, necc ak-d tmeddukař inu.”
\v 38 Netta yarra-dd xas: “Uyur!” Uca ijja i-tt ad traḥ tnayen n iyuren. Nettat \add maca\add* tᵉṭṭef abrid ak-d tmeddukař nnes uca tru x tuɛezriya nnes deg idurar.
\v 39 Imsar, umi qefřen tnayen n iyuren, tareggʷweḥ-dd ɣar babas u netta iqfeř lwaɛd i iwaɛd. Nettat tuɣa \add ɛemmarṣ\add* war tessin uřa d ijj n weryaz. Ammu idweř d lɛada di Israil, \f ◼ \fr 11:39 \fk war tessin\ft - řmeɛna n wawař-a, aqa nettat war tᵉṭṭis ca ak-d weryaz, maca teqqim ammu d taɛzarect.\f*
\v 40 aqa aseggʷas awarni i useggʷas yessis n Israil ad ṭṭfent abrid, ḥima ad idarent i yeǧis n Yaftaḥ, Ajilɛadi, arebɛa n wussan deg useggʷas.
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Yaftaḥ d Ifrayim
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* ttwassmunen iryazen n Ifrayim \add i umenɣi\add* u nitni ẓwan ɣar Zafun. Nnan i Yaftaḥ: “Mayemmi teẓwid ḥima ad temmenɣed ak-d ayt n Ɛammun u war d aneɣ třiɣid ḥima ad nuyur akidek? Neccin ad ac neqqed timessi i taddart nnec tiwa i uzeǧif nnec d cek akides.” \x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt Řqḍ. 8:1\x*
\v 2 Yaftaḥ inna asen: “Necc d řgens inu tuɣa aneɣ deg ijj n umcubbec d ameqqran ak-d ayt n Ɛammun. Řaɣiɣ-dd xawem, \add maca\add* kenniw war dd-tusim ḥima ad ayi tfekkem zeg ufus nsen.
\v 3 \add Umi\add* ẓriɣ, belli kenniw war dd-tusim i usenjem, sebbřeɣ tudart inu uca ẓwiɣ \add L’Urdun\add* ɣar ayt n Ɛammun u SIDI igga ayi ten deg ufus. Mayemmi i dd ɣari tgeɛɛdem ass-a ḥima akidi temmenɣem?”
\v 4 \add Xas uca\add* issmun Yaftaḥ marra iryazen zi Jilɛad uca immneɣ ak-d Ifrayim u iryazen n Jilɛad ɣeřben x Ifrayim, minzi \add iryazen n Ifrayim\add* nnan: “Kenniw d inni yarewřen zeg Ifrayim!”, \add aqa\add* Jilɛad yusa-dd jar Ifrayim d Manassa.
\v 5 Jilɛad iḥewwes imucan n uẓekkwu n L’Urdun \add inni iǧan\add* n Ifrayim. D marra inni yarewřen n Ifrayim nnan: “Ejj ayi ad ẓwiɣ”, xenni sseqsan t iryazen zi Jilɛad: “Ma cek zi Ifrayim?” Mařa netta inna: “Lla!”,
\v 6 \add xenni\add* nnan as: “Ini ‘Cibbulit!’” Inna netta \add xenni\add*: ‘Sibbulit!’ u \add iban-dd\add* netta war izmir ad t inṭeq mliḥ, xenni ṭṭfen t uca nɣin t ɣar imucan n uẓekkwu n L’Urdun. \add Ammu\add* i wḍan tnayen u-rebɛin-ařef n yeryazen n Ifrayim di řweqt nni.
\v 7 Tuɣa Yaftaḥ iḥekkem Israil setta n iseggʷusa. \add Xenni\add* immut Yaftaḥ, Ajilɛadi, u netta ittwanḍeř deg \add ict zi\add* tneddam n Jilɛad.
\b
\s1 Ibṣan, Ilun d Ɛabdun
\m 
\v 8 Awarni as tuɣa \bd Ibṣan\bd* zi Bayt-Laḥm d řqaḍi x Israil.
\v 9 Netta tuɣa ɣares třatin n iḥenjiren u issmeǧec třatin n yessis ɣar barra u i třatin n arrawen nnes ijja i-ten ad awyen třatin n yessis zi barra. Tuɣa netta iḥekkem x Israil sebɛa n iseggʷusa.
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* immut Ibṣan uca ittwanḍeř di Bayt-Laḥm.
\m 
\v 11 Awarni as tuɣa \bd Ilun\bd*, Azabuluni, d řqaḍi x Israil. Netta iḥkem x Israil ɛecra n iseggʷusa. \f ◼ \fr 12:11 \fk Azabuluni\ft - ijjen zi teqbič n Zabulun.\f*
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* immut Ilun, Azabuluni, uca ittwanḍeř di Ayalun di temmurt n Zabulun.
\m 
\v 13 Awarni as tuɣa \bd Ɛabdun\bd*, mmis n Hillal, zi Firɛatun, d řqaḍi x Israil.
\v 14 Netta tuɣa ɣares arebɛin n iḥenjiren d třatin n wayyawen, inni innayen x sebɛin n iɣyař. Netta tuɣa d řqaḍi x Israil tmenya n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 12:14 \xt Řqḍ. 10:4\x*
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* immut Ɛabdun, mmis n Hillel, zi Firɛatun, uca ittwanḍeř di Firɛatun, di temmurt n Ifrayim, x idurar n Ɛamaliq.
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 Axřaq n Camcun
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* arnin ayt n Israil maḥend ad ggen min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. \add Xenni\add* inḍar i-ten SIDI deg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen, \add ijj n řmijař n\add* arebɛin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 13:1 \xt Řqḍ. 2:11; 3:7; 4:1; 6:1; 10:6\x*
\v 2 Tuɣa din ijj n weryaz zi Ṣurɛa, zi řwacun n Dan. Tuɣa qqaren as Manuḥ. Tamɣart nnes tuɣa war ɣares bu tarwa u war dd-tiruw ca.
\v 3 Iban-dd lmalak n SIDI i temɣart-a uca netta inna as: “Xzar, war ɣarem bu tarwa u war dd-tirwud ca, maca ad teksid ddeyset, ad tarwed ijj n uḥenjir.
\v 4 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, ḥḍa ixef nnem! War sess binu uřa d ccrab u war ttᵉtt walu zi marra min inegsen! \x ◘ \xo 13:4 \xt Řxř. 6:2, 3\x*
\v 5 Maɣar xzar, cem ad teksid s ddeyset, ad tarwed ijj n uḥenjir. War d as ittekk řmus x uzeǧif nnes, maɣar aḥenjir ad yarbu ttaj \add n weɛzař\add* n AREBBI zeg uɛeddis n yemmas u netta ad ibda ḥima ad ifekk Israil zeg ufus n Ifilisṭiniyyen.” \x ◘ \xo 13:5 \xt Řxř. 6:5; 1 Ṣm. 1:11\x*
\m 
\v 6 Tamɣart tudef u tessiweř ak-d weryaz nnes, tenna as: “Ijj n Weryaz n AREBBI yusa-dd ɣari. Aɣembub nnes igga am lmalak n AREBBI, issaggʷad aṭṭas, uca necc war t sseqsiɣ manis dd-yusa, u Netta war d ayi inni mammec d as qqaren.
\v 7 Netta inna ayi: ‘Xzar, cem ad teksid s ddeyset, ad tarwed ijj n uḥenjir. War sess binu uřa d ccrab u war ttᵉtt walu min ixemjen, minzi aḥenjir ad yarbu ttaj \add n weɛzař\add* n AREBBI zeg uɛeddis n yemmas ař ass n řmewt nnes.’
\v 8 Uca iẓẓuǧ Manuḥ ɣar SIDI, inna: “A, Sidi inu, ttzawageɣ Cek, ejj aryaz n AREBBI wenni dd tessekked, ad ɣarneɣ dd-yas twařa nneɣnit, maḥend ad aneɣ isscen min ɣa negg ak-d uḥenjir wenni dd ɣa ixeřqen.”
\m 
\v 9 Uca SIDI isřa ɣar Manuḥ u lmalak n AREBBI yusa-dd ict n twařa nneɣnit ɣar temɣart. Nettat teqqim deg iyyar uca aryaz nnes Manuḥ tuɣa war kides iǧi. \f ◼ \fr 13:9 \fk isřa ɣar Manuḥ\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘isřa ɣar tmijja n Manuḥ’.\f*
\v 10 Nettat tqeǧeq u teɛřef, tɛawed aya i weryaz nnes, tenna as: “Xzar, Aryaz nni dd ɣari yusin, iban ayi-dd \add ɛawed\add*.”
\v 11 Ikkar Manuḥ, iḍfar tamɣart nnes. Umi dd-yusa ɣar Weryaz, inna as: “Ma cek d Aryaz nni issiwřen ak-d temɣart inu?” Netta yarra-dd xas: “\add Wah,\add* d Necc.”
\v 12 \add Xenni\add* inna Manuḥ: “Mařa ttwakemmřen xenni wawařen nnec řexxu, min \add i ɣa tiři\add* řqaɛida \add i zi ɣa nuyur\add* ak-d uḥenjir u min \add i ɣa tiři\add* řxedmet nnes?”
\v 13 Inna lmalak n SIDI i Manuḥ: “Tamɣart ad teḥḍa ixef nnes zi marra min d as nniɣ.
\v 14 Nettat war ttᵉtt min dd-ittasen zi tzayart uca war tsess binu uřa d ccrab u war ttᵉtt walu zi marra min inegsen. Ad teḥḍa marra min d as umureɣ.”
\m 
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* inna Manuḥ i lmalak n SIDI: “Ejj aneɣ ad Cek nemneɛ ɣarneɣ \add cwayt danita\add* u ad ac nessewjed ijj n iɣayḍ d ameẓyan zeg iɣayḍen zzat i wudem nnec.”
\v 16 \add Maca\add* lmalak n SIDI inna i Manuḥ: “Mařa texsed ad ayi tmenɛed, war ttᵉtteɣ zeg weɣrum nnec u mařa texsed ad tesswejded ict n tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ, ittxeṣṣa ad tt tqedmed i SIDI.” Minzi Manuḥ war issin, aqa-t d lmalak n SIDI.
\v 17 Uca inna Manuḥ i lmalak n SIDI: “Mammec i d ac qqaren, ḥima ad ac negg ccan, xmi ɣa ittwakemmeř wawař nnec.”
\v 18 Inna as \add maca\add* lmalak n SIDI “Mayemmi d ayi tesseqsid x Yisem inu? Aqa wanita d Řeɛjeb.”
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* iksi Manuḥ ijj n iɣayḍ d ameẓyan zeg iɣayḍen ak-d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* uca iqeddem \add aya\add* x teṣḍart i SIDI. \add Xas uca\add* igga Netta ijj n řeɛjeb umi Manuḥ d temɣart nnes tuɣa xezzaren.
\v 20 Řami tuɣa aceɛɛař n uɛalṭar igeɛɛed deg ujenna, imsar aqa uřa lmalak n SIDI igeɛɛed deg uceɛɛař n uɛalṭar. Manuḥ d temɣart nnes ẓrin aya, wḍan ɣar temmurt x iɣembab nsen.
\m 
\v 21 Ssenni \add maca\add* war dd-ibin lmalak n SIDI ɛad ɣar Manuḥ d temɣart nnes. Xenni issen Manuḥ, belli tuɣa d lmalak n SIDI.
\v 22 Inna Manuḥ i temɣart nnes: “S tidett neccin ad nemmet, minzi neccin neẓra AREBBI.” \x ◘ \xo 13:22 \xt Uf. 33:20; Aɛwd. 5:26; Řqḍ. 6:22, 23\x*
\v 23 Tenna as temɣart nnes: “Mařa SIDI ixs ad aneɣ ineɣ, iři Netta war iksi zeg ufus nneɣ taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* u ad tiři war dd aneɣ ittejji ad nẓar ad nseř qaɛ man aya di řweqt-a.”
\m 
\v 24 Tamɣart turuw-dd ijj n uḥenjir, tegga as \bd Camcun\bd*. Aḥenjir imɣar u SIDI ibarek i-t. \f ◼ \fr 13:24 \fk Camcun\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘am tfuct’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 13:24 \xt Ɛbr. 11:32\x*
\v 25 Uca Arruḥ n SIDI ibda ad t indeh di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar n Dan jar Ṣurɛa d Icta’ul.
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Řemřac n Camcun
\m 
\v 1 Camcun ihwa ɣar Timnata. Di Timnata iẓra ict n temɣart jar yessis n Ifilisṭiniyyen.
\v 2 Umi dd-igeɛɛed \add ɛawed\add*, iḥaja t i babas d yemmas, inna: “Necc ẓriɣ di Timnata ict n temɣart jar yessis n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Xenni řexxu, awyem ayi tt d tamɣart i necc!”
\v 3 Inna as babas uřa d yemmas: “Ma war \add din\add* teǧi ict n temɣart jar yessis n aytmac u jar marra řgens inu umi texsed ad tawyed ict n temɣart zeg Ifilisṭiniyyen i war ittwaxetnen?” Uca inna Camcun i babas: “Awi ayi i-tt i necc, minzi nettat \add d tamɣart\add* tecna di tiṭṭawin inu.”
\v 4 Babas d yemmas war ssinen, aqa man aya \add tuɣa-t\add* zi SIDI, aqa netta yarezzu ssibbet ḍidd i Ifilisṭiniyyen, \add minzi\add* di řweqt nni tuɣa Ifilisṭiniyyen ḥekkmen x Israil.
\m 
\v 5 Ihwa-dd Camcun ɣar Timnata ak-d babas d yemmas. \add Umi\add* iwḍen ɣar imarjaɛen n uḍiř n Timnata, xzar, iffeɣ-dd ɣares ijj n weyrad d ameẓyan izehhar.
\v 6 Arruḥ n SIDI iṭṭef i-t \add ařami\add* t imezzeq axmi ittwamezzeq ijj n iɣayḍ d ameẓyan uca \add d man aya imsar am\add* war ɣares uřa d ict n řḥajjet deg ufus nnes. Netta war iɛawed i babas d yemmas min igga.
\m 
\v 7 Xenni ihwa, issiweř ak-d tmeṭṭut. U nettat tuɣa d \add tamɣart\add* tecna di tiṭṭawin n Camcun.
\v 8 Awarni ca n wussan idweř ɣar din ɛawed, ḥima ad tt yawi \add d tamɣart\add*. Iffeɣ \add zeg webrid\add* ḥima ad ixzar řxecbet n weyrad, u xzar, tuɣa \add din\add* ijj n weyřaf n tzizwa di řxecbet n weyrad, ak-d tamment.
\v 9 Netta iyru tamment deg ifassen, iruḥ uca ittett zzayes am iggur. \add Umi\add* dd-yusa ɣar babas d yemmas, iwca asen zzayes uca uřa d nitni ccin. Maca netta war d asen ini, aqa netta tuɣa ikkes-dd tamment zi řxecbet n weyrad.
\m 
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* ihwa babas ɣar temɣart u Camcun igga dinni ijj n wurar am mammec \add nnumen\add* ad t tteggen iḥudriyyen.
\v 11 \add Umi\add* t ẓrin nitni, imsar, belli iwyen třatin n imɛacaren ḥima akides iřin.
\v 12 Inna asen Camcun: “Ejj ayi ad awem iniɣ ict n tḥajit n twafit. Mařa kenniw tzemmaren ad ayi tt tcarrḥem u ad xas teffɣem di sebɛa n wussan n wurar-a, \add xenni\add* ad awem wceɣ třatin n tikkas d třatin n warruḍ icnan.
\v 13 \add Maca\add* mařa war tzemmarem ad ayi tt tcarrḥem, xenni kenniw ad ayi tewcem třatin n tikkas d třatin n warruḍ icnan.” Nitni nnan as: “Ini aneɣ tḥajit n twafit nnec, neccin nexs ad \add tt\add* nseř!”
\v 14 Netta inna asen: “Macca iffeɣ-dd zeg wenni ittetten u taẓyudi teffeɣ-dd zeg wenni ijehden.” Třata n wussan war zemmaren ad carrḥen tḥajit n twafit \add i d asen inna\add*.
\v 15 Deg wass wiss sebɛa imsar, aqa nnan i temɣart n Camcun: “Ɣwa aryaz nnem maḥend ad aneɣ ifessar tḥajit n twafit niɣ ad am neqqed timessi ak-d taddart n babam. Ma tɛarḍem aneɣ \add da\add*, ḥima ad aneɣ tekksem agřa nneɣ niɣ lla?”
\m 
\v 16 Uca tru temɣart n Camcun zzates, tenna: “Cek aqa tcarrhed ayi waha, war d ayi tᵉttexsed. Cek tennid i tarwa n řgens inu ict n tḥajit n twafit u war d ayi tt tfessared.” Netta yarra-dd xas: “Xzar, war tt nniɣ ɛad uřa i baba uřa i yemma. Mammec i d am tt i ɣa iniɣ i cem?”
\v 17 Nettat maca tru zzates \add marra\add* sebɛa n wussan nni di ggin urar u deg wass wiss sebɛa imsar ařami i d as tt inna, minzi nettat tehweř i-t uca nettat tcarreḥ tḥajit n twafit i tarwa n řgens nnes.
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* nnan as yeryazen n tendint deg wass wiss sebɛa qbeř ma ad teɣři tfuct: “Min iǧan d amiẓid x tamment d min ijehden x weyrad?” \add X uya\add* netta inna asen: “Mařa war tecrizem kenniw s tɛejmit inu, iři kenniw war teffiɣem tḥajit n twafit inu.”
\m 
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* iṭṭef i-t Arruḥ n SIDI uca ihwa ɣar Acqalun uca inɣa třatin n yeryazen u iksi takeccadṭ zzaysen uca iwca arruḍ icnan i yinni issfehmen tḥajit n twafit. Axeyyeq nnes \add maca\add* tuɣa yareqq uca igeɛɛed \add ɛawed\add* ɣar taddart n babas.
\v 20 \add S uya\add* temmewc temɣart nnes i umɛacar nnes, wenni tuɣa i-t iɛacaren.
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Axřef n Camcun di ṭṭweɛ n temɣart Tafiliṣtinect nnes zi Timna
\m 
\v 1 Awarni ca n wussan, deg wussan n tmeyra n irden, imsar, issijji Camcun x temɣart nnes, yiwi akides ijj n iɣayḍ d ameẓyan zeg iɣayḍen, inna \add i babas\add*: “Ejj ayi ad adfeɣ ɣar temɣart inu deg wexxam!” \add Maca\add* babas war t ijji ad yadef.
\v 2 Inna babas: “S tidett necc nniɣ \add deg yixef inu\add*, cek tɛiffed tt, s uyenni wciɣ tt i umɛacar nnec. Ma war teǧi učmas tamaẓuẓt ɛad tecna xas? Ejj i-tt ad ɣarek tiři deg wemcan nnes.”
\v 3 \add Maca\add* Camcun inna asen: “Twařat-a ad iřiɣ d acemrař zi jjihet n Ifilisṭiniyyen, mařa ggiɣ daysen min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan.”
\m 
\v 4 U Camcum yuyur, iymar-dd teřt-mya n iceɛbawen. Iksi iṣefḍawen uca issneqřeb i-ten ijj x wenneɣni s ikennasen \add nsen\add* uca di řwesṭ, jar tnayen n ikennasen, icedd ijj n uṣefḍaw.
\v 5 Netta issarɣ iṣefḍawen uca ijja \add iceɛbawen\add* ad uyuren deg imendi ibedden n Ifilisṭiniyyen. Ammu issarɣ icuwwafen \add n imendi\add* d imendi ibedden, uřa d iyyaren n uzemmur.
\m 
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* nnan Ifilisṭiniyyen: “Wi iggin aya?” Nnan; “Aqa d Camcun, aḍeggʷař n weryaz. zi Timnata, minzi wanita yiwi as tamɣart nnes, iwca i-tt i umɛacar nnes.” \add Xenni\add* geɛɛden Ifilisṭiniyyen uca qqden timessi i temɣart d babas.
\v 7 \add Xas uca\add* inna asen Camcun: “Mařa kenniw teggim ammu, xenni ḥsen ad zzaywem ntaqmeɣ \add d amezwaru\add* uca awarni aya waha ad ssbeddeɣ amenɣi.”
\v 8 Netta yarẓa asen iɣsan x tnayen, aqa iwta i-ten s ict n tecti d tameqqrant. \add Xenni\add* ihwa, yuyur izdeɣ deg ifri n teṣḍart n Ɛiṭam. \f ◼ \fr 15:8 \fk yarẓa asen ixsan x tnayen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘aḍar x tmeṣṣaḍt’.\f*
\m 
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* geɛɛden Ifilisṭiniyyen uca wtin iqiḍan nsen di Yahuda uca areyycen ixef nsen ař Laḥi.
\v 10 Iryazen n Yahuda nnan: “Mayemmi i dd xaneɣ tgeɛɛdem?” Nitni arrin-dd nnan: “Neccin ngeɛɛed, ḥima ad ncarf Camcun maḥend ad kides negg am mammec i kidneɣ igga netta.”
\m 
\v 11 Uca hwan teřt-ařaf n yeryazen zi Yahuda ɣar ifri n teṣḍart n Ɛiṭam, nnan i Camcun: “Ma war tessined cek, aqa Ifilisṭiniyyen ḥekkmen xaneɣ? Mayemmi d aneɣ teggid aya?” Netta yarra-dd xasen: “Am mammec akidi ggin, ammu akidsen i ɣa ggeɣ.”
\v 12 Nitni nnan as: “Neccin nehwa-dd ḥima ad cek ncarf u ad cek negg deg ifassen n Ifilisṭiniyyen.” \add Xenni\add* inna Camcun: “Jaǧem ayi, aqa kenniw war xafi thejjmem.”
\v 13 Nitni ssiwřen akides, nnan as: “\add Man aya\add* war ittiři, maca neccin ad cek ncarf u ad cek negg deg ufus nsen, maca s tidett war cek neneqq.” Uca carfen t nitni s tnayen n tseɣwin d timaynutin uca nedhen t zeg ifri ɣar sennej.
\v 14 \add Řami\add* yiweḍ ɣar Laḥi, ffɣen-dd ɣares Ifilisṭiniyyen s iɣuyyan \add n umenɣi\add*. \add Řexdenni\add* iṭṭef i-tt Arruḥ n SIDI uca tiseɣwin nni ɣar iɣaǧen nnes dewřent am tiffest i ittwasscemḍen s tmessi d iceddiyyen nnes fesyen zeg iɣaǧen nnes.
\v 15 Netta yufa ijj n yiɣes n uqabsi d ṭṭri n ijj n weɣyuř. \add Xenni\add* isswiẓẓeḍ afus nnes, iḥart xas uca inɣa zzayes ařef n yeryazen.
\v 16 Inna Camcun: “S yijj n yiɣes n uqabsi n weɣyuř, ijj n uɛurric, tnayen n iɛurricen, aqa s yijj n iɣes n uqabsi n teɣyuč nɣiɣ ařef n yeryazen.”
\v 17 Imsar, umi ikemmeř awař nnes, inḍar iɣes n uqabsi zeg ufus nnes uca igga as i wemcan nni Ramat-Laḥi, \add ‘Řgeɛɛdet n yiɣes n uqabsi’\add*.\f ◼ \fr 15:17 \fk Ramat-Laḥi\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘řgaɛɛdet n yiɣes n uqabsi’.\f*
\m 
\v 18 \add Řexdenni\add* tuɣa dayes afadi aṭṭas uca iřaɣa ɣar SIDI inna: “Cek tewcid i umsexxar nnec asenjem-a ameqqran. Ma \add xenni\add* ittxeṣṣa ad mmteɣ s ufadi, ad wḍiɣ deg ifassen n ina inni war ixetnen?” \x ◘ \xo 15:18 \xt 1 Ṣm. 17:26, 36; 2 Ṣm. 1:2\x*
\v 19 \add Xas uca\add* issfeǧeq AREBBI aḥfur n Laḥi, ffɣen-dd zzayes waman. Netta isu uca buḥbeř nnes idweř-dd uca idweř-dd ɣar tudart. X uya igga as \add i tařa nni\add* ‘Ɛayn-Haqurey’, \add ixs ad yini ‘Tařa n wenni ittřaɣan’\add*. Tanita aqa-tt di Laḥi ař ass-a.
\v 20 Tuɣa netta d řqaḍi x Israil deg wussan n Ifilisṭiniyyen, ɛicrin n iseggʷusa.
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Camcun di Ɣazza
\m 
\v 1 Umi iṭṭef Camcun \add abrid\add* ɣar Ɣazza, iẓra dinni ict n temɣart n farq-ccɣeř, uca yudef ɣares.
\v 2 \add Xenni\add* ittwanna i ayt n Ɣazza: “Camcun aqa-t da!” Innḍen as-dd uca ḥḍan ǧiřet tmun ɣar tewwart n tendint. Ǧiřet tmun ssqaren, nnan: “Ɣar tuffut n wass ad t neneɣ.”
\v 3 Camcun \add maca\add* iqqim izzeř \add iṭṭeṣ\add* ař azyen n ǧiřet. \add Xenni\add* ikkar-dd deg wezyen n ǧiřet, iṭṭef tiwwura n tendint ak-d řeḍruf \add ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart\add*, iqřeɛ i tent i-dd akl-d weɛmud i ubelleɛ, igga i-tent x tɣarḍin nnes uca yarbu tent ɣar tqiccet n wedrar nni \add iǧan\add* qibač i Ḥabrun.
\b
\s1 Camcun d Dalila
\m 
\v 4 Awarni as, imsar iɛceq ict n temɣart ɣar teɣzart n Suraq, qqaren as Dalila.
\v 5 Uca řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen usin-dd ɣares, nnan as: “Ɣwa i-t, u xzar \add ad tafed\add* zi manis ɣares jjehd-a tameqqrant u mammec xas i ɣa nzemmar. \add Xenni\add* ad t ncarf, ḥima ad t neṭṭef. \bd Neccin\bd* ad am newc kuř ijj \add zzayneɣ\add* ařef u-mya n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart.”
\v 6 Xas uca tenna Dalila i Camcun: “Ini ayi maca, zi manis ɣarek jjehd-a ameqqran d mammec zemmaren ad cek carfen ḥima ad tᵉttwaṭṭfed.”
\v 7 Inna as Camcun: “Mařa carfen ayi s sebɛa n iẓewran ṭṭri \add zeg weysum\add* nni war yuẓiɣen ɛad, xenni ad dewřeɣ arxuɣ am \add kuř\add* ijj n bnadem nneɣni.”
\v 8 Řbacat \add n tneddam\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen iwyen as-dd sebɛa n iẓewran d ṭṭri \add zeg weysum\add* nni war yuẓiɣen ɛad u nettat tcarf i-t zzaysent.
\v 9 \add Deg ijj n umur\add* tuɣa ɣares ḥed di texxamt n daxeř iṭṭef aḥeṭṭu. Tenna as: “\add A\add* Camcun, Ifilisṭiniyyen \add usin-dd\add* xak!” \add Xenni\add* iqḍuw iẓewran am mammec ittqeṭṭas bnadem afiřu n tiffest axmi tt teřqef tmessi. Uca \add ssir n\add* jjehd nnes war idwiř ittwassen.
\m 
\v 10 \add Xas uca\add* tenna Dalila i Camcun: “Xzar, tcemted ayi u tessxarrqed xafi. Ini ayi maca řexxu, s min zi zemmaren ad cek carfen.”
\v 11 Netta inna as: “Mařa carfen ayi s tseɣwin n jdid war ttwassxedment \add ɛemmarṣ\add*, ad dewřeɣ arxuɣ am \add kuř\add* ijj n bnadem nneɣni.”
\v 12 Uca Dalila teksi tiseɣwin timaynutin tcarf i-t zzaysent u tenna as: “A Camcun, Ifilisṭiniyyen \add usin-dd\add* xak!”, \add deg umur d ijjen\add* tuɣa ḥed deg ict n texxamt n daxeř iṭṭef aḥeṭṭu. \add Xenni\add* iqeṭṭes tiseɣwin zeg iɣaǧen nnes am yijj n ufiřu.
\m 
\v 13 Xas uca tenna Dalila i Camcun: “Xzar, cek tcemted ayi u tessxarrqed xafi. Ini ayi maca, s min zi zemmaren ad cek carfen?” Netta inna as: “Mařa cem tmuded sebɛa n tmuzarin x uzeǧif inu ak-d wexmar \add n ddebbuz n txeyyaḍt\add*!”
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* nettat tessemted tent s yijj n umesmir, tenna as: “A Camcun, Ifilisṭiniyyen \add usin-dd\add* xak!” \add Xenni\add* ifaq-dd zeg yiḍeṣ nnes, ikkes-dd ddebbuz n txeyyaḍt d ufiřu.
\m 
\v 15 \add Xas uca\add* tenna as: “Mammec tzemmared ad tinid: ‘Necc ttexseɣ cem!’, mařa uř nnec war ɣari iǧi? Řexxu tcemted ayi třata n twařawin u war d ayi tennid zi manis ɣarek jjehd-a ameqqran.”
\v 16 Uca imsar, umi nettat tegga xas aɣiř s wawařen nnes u tehweř i-t marra ussan, idweř řeɛmar nnes di řeḥṣaret ař řmewt.
\v 17 Netta issargeb i-tt marra x wuř nnes, inna as: “Ijj n řmus i uḥeffi ɛemmarṣ war ɣari dd-yusi x uzeǧif inu, minzi necc arebbuɣ ttaj \add n weɛzař\add* zeg uɛeddis n yemmas. Mařa ittwaḥeff ucuwwaf inu, xenni ad ayi iffeɣ jjehd inu, ad dewřeɣ arxuɣ am kuř bnadem \add nneɣni\add*.”
\v 18 \add Umi\add* teẓra Dalila, belli aqa netta issargeb i-tt marra x wuř nnes, nettat tessekk ɣar řbacat n \add tneddam n\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen, tenna: “Asem-dd twařa-ya da, minzi issargeb ayi marra sirr n wuř nnes.” Řbacat n \add tneddam n\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen geɛɛden-dd ɣares, iwyen-dd akidsen \add řweznat n\add* nnuqart deg ufus nsen.
\v 19 Nettat tejja Camcun ad iṭṭeṣ x ifadden nnes, třaɣa i weryaz, tqess as sebɛa n tmuzarin x uzeǧif nnes uca tebda nettat tᵉṭṭef i-t ɣares uca jjehd nnes iffeɣ zzayes.
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* tenna: “A Camcun, Ifilisṭiniyyen \add usin-dd\add* xak!” Netta ifaq-dd zeg yiḍeṣ, inna: “Twařa-ya ad arxuɣ, ad ssfekkeɣ ixef inu”, \add minzi\add* netta war issin, aqa SIDI tuɣa ismeḥ dayes.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* ṭṭfen t Ifilisṭiniyyen, qeřɛen as tiṭṭawin uca nedhen t ɣar Ɣazza, carfen t s tnayen n ssnaseř n nnḥas u netta idweř issunnuḍ tasirt di řeḥbes.
\v 22 \add Maca\add* acuwwaf n uzeǧif nnes idweř imeqqar deɣya awarni řami i d as ḥeffen.
\b
\s1 Řmewt n Camcun
\m 
\v 23 Řbacat n \add tneddam n\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen munen, ḥima ad qeddmen ict n tɣarṣt d tameqqrant i Dajun, arebbi nsen, uřa i řefraḥet, uca nnan: “Arebbi nneɣ iwca aneɣ Camcun, řeɛdu nneɣ, deg ifassen nneɣ.”
\v 24 \add Umi\add* t iẓra řgens, ssemɣaren arebbi nsen, maɣar nnan: “Arebbi nneɣ igga řeɛdu nneɣ deg ufus nneɣ: netta, wenni ixřan tammurt nneɣ d wenni inɣin zzayneɣ aṭṭas!”
\v 25 Uca imsar, umi uř nsen tuɣa ifarḥ, nnan: “Řaɣam i Camcun, ḥima ad aneɣ issfarḥ.” Uca řaɣan-dd x Camcun zi řeḥbes uca sstehzan zzayes zzat i wudem nsen uca jjin t ad ibedd jar ipilaren.
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* inna Camcun i uḥenjir wenni t inedhen zeg ufus: “Ewc ayi cwayt n arraḥet. Xseɣ ad ḥadiɣ ipilaren i yarebbun taddart, maḥend ad xasen senndeɣ.”
\v 27 Taddart tuɣa teccur s yeryazen d temɣarin. Tuɣa din \add ɛawed\add* marra řbacat n \add tneddam n\add* Ifilisṭiniyyen. X tzeqqa \add iwaṭan\add* tuɣa \add qqimen\add* amenni teřt-ařaf n yeryazen d temɣarin nni xezzaren umi ittɣennen Camcun.
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa Camcun ɣar SIDI, inna: “Sidi inu, SIDI, xarreṣ dayi. Ewc ayi mɣir twařa-ya waha jjehd inu, \add a\add* AREBBI, ḥima ad ntaqmeɣ ixef inu zeg Ifilisṭiniyyen di ssibbet n tiṭṭawin inu deg ict n twařa.” \x ◘ \xo 16:28 \xt Ɛbr. 11:32\x*
\v 29 Uca iṭṭef Camcun tnayen n ipilaren i \add iǧan\add* di řwesṭ i yarbun u min xef tsenned taddart, \add iṭṭef\add* ijj n upilar s ufus nnes afusi d wenneɣni s ufus nnes azeřmaḍ.
\v 30 Xas uca Camcun inna: “Ejj řeɛmar inu ad immet ak-d Ifilisṭiniyyen!”, u netta iɣnes ixef nnes ɣar zzat s \add marra\add* jjehd nnes uca tewḍa taddart x řbacat \add n tneddam\add* u x marra řgens i dayes tuɣa iǧan. Tuɣa qedda n yinni i inɣa s řmewt nnes d ameqqran x yinni tuɣa inɣa umi tuɣa iddar.
\v 31 Aytmas d marra taddart n babas hwan-dd u ssgeɛɛden t, iwyen t u neḍřen t jar Ṣurɛa d Icta’ul deg wenḍeř n babas Manuḥ. Tuɣa netta d řqaḍi x Israil ɛicrin n iseggʷusa.
\b
\b
\c 17
\s1 Mixa d řexyař nnes n ṣṣanam
\m 
\v 1 Ijj n weryaz tuɣa izeddeɣ x idurar n Ifrayim, qqaren as Mixa-Yahu.
\v 2 Netta inna i yemmas: “Ařef u-mya n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart i d am ittwakksen, i xasent tennid ict n nneɛřet i zi tneṭqed deg imezzuɣen inu, xzar, nnuqart nni aqa-tt ɣari, necc ksiɣ tt.” Yemmas tenna: “Ad ittwabarek mmi zi SIDI!”
\v 3 Netta yarra ařef u-mya n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart i yemmas uca yemmas tenna as: “Nnuqart ssqeddseɣ tt i SIDI zeg ufus inu i mmi ḥima ad zzayes igg ijj n řexyař ineqcen d ijj n řexyař ifesyen. \add Xenni\add* řexxu ad ac tt arreɣ.”
\v 4 Netta \add maca\add* yarra nnuqart \add ɛawed\add* i yemmas. \add Xenni\add* teksi yemmas mitayen n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart u tewca i-tent i yijj n wemziř n wureɣ, wenni zzayes iggin ijj n řexyař ineqcen d yijj n řexyař ifesyen uca ggin tent di taddart n Mixa-Yahu.
\v 5 Tuɣa Mixa ɣares ict n taddart n arebbi u netta igga ijj n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* d řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam uca iřeqqem ijjen zeg iḥenjiren nnes ad ɣares yiři d akehhan.
\m 
\v 6 Deg wussan nni war din tuɣi ajeǧid di Israil. Kuř ijj ittegg min \add iǧan\add* nican di tiṭṭawin nnes. \x ◘ \xo 17:6 \xt Řqḍ. 18:1; 21:25\x*
\v 7 Di Bayt-Laḥm di Yahuda tuɣa din ijj n webřiɣ zi řwacun n Yahuda. Netta tuɣa d ijj n Ulawi, tuɣa izeddeɣ dinni d abarrani.
\v 8 Aryaz-a iffeɣ zi tendint nni, zi Bayt-Laḥm di Yahuda, ḥima ad izdeɣ am ubarrani mani ma izemmar ad yaf \add amcan\add*. X webrid nnes yiweḍ ɣar idurar n Ifrayim ɣar taddart n Mixa.
\v 9 Mixa isseqsa t: “Manis i dd-tusid cek?” Netta yarra-dd xas: “Necc d Alawi zi Bayt-Laḥm di Yahuda. Necc ggureɣ, ḥima ad zedɣeɣ mani ma i ɣa yafeɣ \add amcan\add*.”
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* inna as Mixa: “Qqim ɣari uca tiřid ayi d baba d akehhan! Necc ad ac wceɣ ɛecra n \add uqiyyat n\add* nnuqart d ca n werruḍ d řeɛweč.” Uca Alawi yuyur akides.
\v 11 Alawi yarḍa xas deg wawař ḥima ad iqqim ak-d weryaz u abřiɣ tuɣa i Mixa am yijjen zeg arraw nnes.
\v 12 Mixa iccur Alawi uca idweř webřiɣ d akehhan i netta uca iqqim di taddart n Mixa.
\v 13 Uca inna Mixa: “Řexxu ssneɣ necc, aqa SIDI ad ayi igg řxar, maɣar necc ɣari Alawi wanita d akehhan.”
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Taqbič n Dan teṭṭef Layic d tasɣart nnes
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan nni war din tuɣi ajeǧid di Israil u deg wussan nni tuɣa taqbič n Dan tarezzu tasɣart i yixef nnes maḥend ad dayes tezdeɣ, minzi war d as dd-tekkar \add ɛad\add* tesɣart jar tqebbař n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 18:1 \xt Řqḍ. 17:6; 21:25\x*
\v 2 Ssekken ayt n Dan zi řwacun nsen xemsa n yeryazen zi marra ṭṭrufa nsen, iryazen \add nni\add* d ayt n umenɣi inni dd-yusin zi Ṣurɛa d Icta’ul, ḥima ad arzun řexbar x temmurt, ad dayes yarzun. Nitni nnan asen: “Uyurem, arzum tammurt!” Usin-dd ɣar idurar n Ifrayim ɣar taddart n Mixa uca ssensen dinni.
\v 3 \add Umi\add* \add iwḍen\add* nitni ɣar taddart n Mixa, ɛeqřen x tmijja n webřiɣ zeg ayt n Lawi, uca ffɣen \add zeg webrid\add* ɣares, nnan as: “Min cek i da dd-yiwyen u min i da tᵉttegged u min i da tarezzud cek?”
\v 4 Netta yarra-dd xasen: “Ta d ta i igga Mixa akidi. Netta icra ayi u ammu i dewřeɣ necc d akehhan nnes.”
\v 5 Nitni nnan as: “Seqsa aneɣ AREBBI, maḥend ad nessen, ma abrid i ɣa nuyur, ad yiři mliḥ.”
\v 6 Yarra-dd xasen ukehhan: “Uyurem di řehna! Abrid i texsem ad t tekkem, aqa-t \add yarezmen\add* zzat i \add tiṭṭawin n\add* SIDI.”
\m 
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* ruḥen xemsa n yeryazen nni, iwḍen ɣar Layic. Nitni ẓrin aqa řgens izdeɣ dayes di řaman am mammec t tuɣa d lqaɛida ɣar ayt n Ṣidun, s řhudnet u di řaman. Tuɣa war din uřa d ijj di temmurt wenni iḥṣaren x \add yijjen\add* di ca n řḥajjet niɣ iṭṭef ca s řexcunet. Nitni tuɣa iggʷejen aṭṭas x ayt n Ṣidun u war ɣarsen tuɣi walu uřa ak-d ijj n bnadem.
\v 8 Uca usin-dd ɣar aytmatsen di Ṣurɛa d Icta’ul uca nnan asen aytmatsen: “Man \add awař i\add* ɣarwem?”
\v 9 Nitni arrin-dd xasen: “Kkarem, jjem ad ngeɛɛed, minzi neẓra tammurt, u xzar, aqa-tt tecna aṭṭas. Ma xenni \add texsem\add* ad teqqimem tᵉttarsam ammu? War tteɛgizem ca maḥend ad tadfem ɣar temmurt ḥima ad tt tᵉṭṭfem d řwart.
\v 10 Mařa kenniw ad tawḍem din, \add xenni\add* ad tafem ijj n řgens \add izeddɣen\add* di řaman uca tammurt tewseɛ aṭṭas ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen, minzi AREBBI igga awem tt deg ufus nwem, aqa-t d ijj n wemcan mani war d as ittxeṣṣi walu n min iǧan x temmurt.”
\m 
\v 11 \add Xas uca\add* kksen iqiḍan nsen ssenni, zi řaǧ n Dan zi Ṣurɛa d Icta’ul, setta mya n yeryazen ḥezzmen s řesnaḥ.
\v 12 Nitni geɛɛden uca wtin iqiḍan nsen ɣar Qaryat-Yaɛarim di Yahuda. X uya qqaren as i wemcan nni ‘Maxan-Dan’ ař ass-a. Xzar, aqa-tt awarni i Qaryat-Yaɛarim. \f ◼ \fr 18:12 \fk Maxan-Dan\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘tesqift n Dan’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 18:12 \xt Řqḍ. 13:25\x*
\v 13 Ssenni ffɣen, ɛdun ɣar idurar n Ifrayim iwḍen ɣar taddart n Mixa.
\v 14 \add Xenni\add* ssiwřen xemsa n yeryazen, inni tuɣa igguren ḥima ad bergen tammurt n Layic, nnan i aytmatsen: “Ma tessnem, aqa di tudrin nni aqa din ijj n upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* d řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam d ijj n řexyař ineqcen d ijj n řexyař ifesyen? Xenni řexxu, tessnem min xawem ad t teggem.”
\m 
\v 15 \add Řexdenni\add* ffɣen \add zeg webrid nsen\add*, usin-dd ɣar taddart n webřiɣ, ɣar taddart n weryaz zeg ayt n Lawi, ɣar taddart n Mixa, uca sseqsan x mammec iǧa.
\v 16 Setta-mya n yeryazen zeg ayt n Dan i iḥezzmen s řesnaḥ nsen, qqimen bedden ɣar wadaf n tewwart.
\v 17 Xemsa n yeryazen, inni tuɣa iffɣen ḥima ad bergagen tammurt, geɛɛden, udfen u iwyen řexyař ineqcen d upalṭu \add n ukehhan\add* d řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam d řexyař ifesyen. Akehhan iqqim ibedd ɣar uqemmum n tewwart ak-d setta-mya n yeryazen iḥezzmen s řesnaḥ.
\v 18 \add Xemsa\add* ina udfen ɣar taddart n Mixa, kksen řexyař ineqcen d upalṭu n ukehhan d řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam d řexyař ifesyen. \add Xenni\add* inna asen ukehhan: “Min din tᵉtteggem?”
\v 19 Nitni nnan as: “Susem, sars afus nnec x uqemmum nnec, uyur akidneɣ u dweř d baba d akehhan nneɣ! Min iḥřan, mařa cek d akehhan di taddart n ijj n weryaz waha niɣ mařa cek d akehhan i yict n teqbič d yijj n řaǧ di Israil?”
\v 20 \add Řexdenni\add* ifarḥ wuř n weryaz nni uca iksi apalṭu n ukehhan d řexyařat timeẓyanin n l’aṣnam d řexyař ineqcen uca yudef jar řgens.
\v 21 Uca ɛeqben nitni, ffɣen uca nedhen iḥenjiren d řmař d ddquřat akidsen ɣar zzat.
\m 
\v 22 Umi nitni tuɣa iggʷejen aṭṭas x taddart n Mixa, řaɣan-dd i yeryazen di tudrin yudsen x taddart n Mixa, ḥima ad munen uca nitni xeccen x ayt n Dan.
\v 23 Nitni řaɣan awarni i ayt n Dan, \add maca\add* ina nnqeřben azeǧif nsen, nnan i Mixa: “Min cek yuɣin? Mayemmi třaɣid ḥima ad ttwassmunen \add marra\add*?”
\v 24 Inna netta: “Kenniw tekksem xafi irebbiten inu i ggiɣ uřa d akehhan uca tuyurem. Min ɣari řexxu ɛad? Mammec teggim ɛad teqqarem ayi: ‘Min cek yuɣin?’”
\v 25 Ayt n Dan nnan as: “Ɣarek ad nseř i tmijja nnec ɣarneɣ niɣ \add izemmar\add* ad xawem wḍan iryazen yewɛaren u iři \add ad taɣ\add* ad iweddar řeɛmar nnec uřa d řeɛmur n taddart nnec.”
\v 26 Uca uyuren ayt n Dan deg webrid nsen uca umi iẓra Mixa belli nitni tuɣa jehden xas, inneqřeb, yareggʷeḥ ɣar taddart nnes.
\m 
\v 27 Nitni \add maca\add* iwyen min iggin Mixa uřa d akehhan wenni tuɣa ɣares \add ittsexxaren\add*. Nitni iwḍen ɣar Layic, ɣar ijj n řgens \add izeddɣen\add* di řhudnet d řaman uca nɣin ten s řeqḍeɛ n ssif u sscemḍen tandint s tmessi.
\v 28 War din uřa d ijjen \add izemmar\add* ad ifekk, minzi Layic tuɣa tiggʷwej aṭṭas x Ṣidun u war tuɣi ɣarsen walu uřa ak-d ijj n bnadem. Tuɣa-tt di řewḍa n teɣzurt nni ɣar Bayt-Raḥub. Awarni uya bnan tandint \add ɛawed\add* uca zeddɣen dayes.
\v 29 Nitni qqaren as i tendint ‘Dan’, x yisem n babatsen Dan, wenni dd-ittwarwen i Israil. Maca zic tandint tuɣa qqaren as Layic. \x ◘ \xo 18:29 \xt Yac. 19:47\x*
\m 
\v 30 Ayt n Dan ssbedden řexyař ineqcen i yixef nsen. Uca Yahunatan, mmis n Jarcum, mmis n Musa, netta ak-d iḥenjiren nnes, tuɣa aten d ikehhanen n teqbič n Dan ař ass i di tᵉttwandeh temmurt ɣar lmenfa. \f ◼ \fr 18:30 \fk mmis n Musa\ft - aqa neccin nᵉttaf di řmaxṭuṭat n Imasuritiyyen, inni iǧan d imariren n Wudayen, isem n Manassa deg wemcan n yisem n Musa. Waxxa amenni azyen ameqqran n yenni arezzun s jjehd deg Wedlis Iqeddsen n SIDI AREBBI qqaren belli isem n Manassa war yuran danita am mammec nneɣni umi lḥarf ‘nun’ ɣares ijj n ccekl ifarzen, war iǧi am mammec t yuran deg imucan nneɣni. S uyenni ittɣiř asen aqa Imasuritiyyen arnin lḥarf ‘nun’ maɣar nitni war xsen ad ddeǧen isem n Musa s weɛbed n laṣnam am mammec i t igga Yahunatan d tarwa nnes.\f*
\v 31 Nitni tuɣa ssbedden řexyař ineqcen n Mixa, tenni igga, zzat i yixef nsen marra ussan min tekka Taddart n AREBBI teǧa di Cilu.
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 Řefḍiḥet i iggin ayt n Binyamin
\m 
\v 1 Deg wussan nni, umi war din tuɣi ajeǧid di Israil, tuɣa din ijj n Ulawi izeddeɣ d abarrani \add deg ijj n wemcan\add* ɣar iɣezdisen n idurar n Ifrayim. Netta yiwi ict n temɣart d tayya zi Bayt-Laḥm di Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 19:1 \xt Řqḍ. 17:6; 18:1; 21:25\x*
\v 2 \add Maca\add* tayya nnes tedweř tessefḍeḥ ixef nnes umi ɣares tt tuɣa uca tesmeḥ dayes, teɛqeb ɣar taddart n babas di Bayt-Laḥm di Yahuda. Dinni teqqim aṭṭas n wussan, arebɛa n iyuren.
\m 
\v 3 \add Xenni\add* ikkar weryaz, iḍfar i-tt ḥima ad kis issiweř s wuř nnes maḥend ad tt-i-dd-issareggʷeḥ. Tuɣa amsexxar nnes ameẓyan akides d ict n tyuya n yeɣyař. Uca nettat tiwyi i-t ɣar taddart n babas. \add Umi\add* t iẓra babas n tḥenjirt ifarḥ řami kides i ɣa immeřqa.
\v 4 Aḍeggʷař nnes, babas n tḥenjirt, igga xas \add aṭṭas\add* aɣiř maḥend akides iqqim třata n wussan. Nitni ccin, swin u ssensen dinni.
\v 5 Imsar deg wass wiss arebɛa, aqa nitni faqen zic ɣar tuffut u netta ikkar ixs ad yuyur. \add Xenni\add* inna babas n tḥenjirt i wesři nnes: “Semḥeḍ ixef nnec s yijj n uřeqquz n weɣrum, xenni ad taf tzemmarem ad tuyurem.”
\v 6 Nitni qqimen, ccin, swin s tnayen idsen nsen. \add Xenni\add* inna babas n tḥenjirt i weryaz: “Ttzawgeɣ, qqim da, ad tessensed uca ad ifarḥ wuř nnec.”
\v 7 Aryaz ikkar ḥima ad yuyur, \add maca\add* aḍeggʷař nnes ikellef xas, igga xas aɣiř ḥima ad dinni issens ɛawed.
\v 8 Deg wass wiss xemsa ikkar zic ɣar tuffut ḥima ad yuyur. Inna babas n tḥenjirt: “Arni semḥeḍ uř nnec!” U nitni qqimen ttrajan ař ɣa iɛdu wass uca ccin tnayen idsen munen.
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* ikkar weryaz ḥima ad yuyur, netta ak-d tayya nnes d umsexxar nnes. Aḍeggʷař nnes, babas n tḥenjirt, inna: “Xzar, ass ggur ad iɛdu tiweḍ-dd tmeddit, ttzawgeɣ sensem da. Xzar, sfarḥ uř nnec u kkarem tiwecca zic maḥend ad tᵉṭṭfem abrid ɣar tqiḍunt nnec.”
\v 10 \add Maca\add* aryaz war ixs ca \add ɛad\add* ad issens. Ikkar uca yuyur, yiweḍ ař qibač Yabus, tenni d Urcalim, u tuɣa ict n tyuya n yeɣyař bardɛen d tayya nnes aqa-tt akides.
\v 11 \add Umi\add* ten \add tuɣa\add* nitni ɣar Yabus, tuɣa ass ad iɛdu. \add Xenni\add* inna umsexxar i bab nnes: “Uyur, ad da nḍar di tendint-a n Iyabusiyyen, ad dayes nessens.”
\v 12 \add Maca\add* sidi nnes yarra-dd xas: “Neccin war nettmeyyiř ɣar ict n tendint taɣribt, tenni war iǧin n ayt n Israil, \add maca\add* ad narni ad nuyur ɣar Jibɛa.”
\v 13 Netta inna \add ɛawed\add* i umsexxar nnes: “As-dd, ejj aneɣ \add ad narzu\add* ad naweḍ ɣar ijj zeg imucan nni, ad nessens di Jibɛa niɣ di Rama.”
\m 
\v 14 Nitni arnin uyuren u teɣři xasen tfuct umi ten-tuɣa nitni ɣar Jibɛa nni \add iǧan\add* n Binyamin.
\v 15 Uca ssfarɣen \add zeg webrid\add*, ḥima ad adfen ɣar din maḥend ad ssensen di Jibɛa. \add Umi\add* ɣar din yudef, iqqim deg wazzay n tendint, minzi war ten issidef ḥed ɣar taddart maḥend ad ssensen.
\v 16 Uca xzar, ɣar tmeddit iɛqeb-dd yijj n uwessar zi řxedmet nnes zeg iyyar. Tuɣa aryaz nni \add ɛawed\add* zeg idurar n Ifrayim, \add maca\add* izdeɣ am abarrani di Jibɛa, maca imezdaɣ n temmurt nni tuɣa aten d ayt n Binyamin.
\v 17 Issgeɛɛed netta tamuɣři nnes, ixzar aryaz nni tuɣa dd-ikkin d abrid deg wazzay n tendint. Awessar inna: “Mani ɣa tuyured u manis i dd-tusid?”
\v 18 Inna as netta: “Neccin neffeɣ-dd zi Bayt-Laḥm ař ṭṭarf qaɛ ḍeffar x idurar n Ifrayim, ssenni i dd-usiɣ. Necc tuɣa uyureɣ ɣar Bayt-Laḥm di Yahuda, uca \add řexxu\add* ggureɣ ɣar Taddart n SIDI uca war da uřa d ijj wenni ixsen ad ayi issidef ɣar taddart nnes,
\v 19 waxxa neccin ɣarneɣ řum d řeɛřef i yeɣyař nneɣ uřa d aɣrum d binu i necc, i tayya nnec u i uḥudri nni iǧan ɣar imsexxaren nnec. War d aneɣ ixeṣṣ walu.”
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* inna uwessar: “Ad kik yiři řehna! Maca min i d ac iqqimen, aqa-t ɣari, mɣir ittxeṣṣa war tᵉttnusid deg wazzay.”
\m 
\v 21 Netta issidef i-t ɣar taddart nnes, iwca řeɛřef i iɣyař u nitni ssirden iḍaren nsen, ccin swin.
\m 
\v 22 Di řweqt d ict řami ifarḥ wuř nsen, xzar, deɣya nnḍen-dd yeryazen n tendint i taddart - iryazen nni d ayt i war isekkwin - uca ssqarqben di tewwart. Nitni ssiwřen ak-d weryaz awessar, bab n taddart, nnan: “Suffeɣ-dd aryaz, wenni dd-yudfen ɣar taddart nnec, ɣar barra, neccin nexs akides newḍa.” \x ◘ \xo 19:22 \xt Amz. 19:4-1; Ḥuc. 9:9; 10:9\x*
\v 23 Aryaz, bab n taddart, iffeɣ-dd ɣarsen, inna asen: “Lla, a aytma, war tteggem ca tuɛɛefna, awarni řami dd-yudef weryaz-a řexxu ɣar taddart inu. Ɣarwem ad teggem řefḍiḥet am tanita.
\v 24 Xzar, yeǧi d taɛzarect d tayya nnes ad ɣarwem tent ssuffɣeɣ. Sehwam tent u ggem akidsent min texsem, maca deg weryaz-a war tteggem řefḍiḥet am tanita.”
\m 
\v 25 \add Maca\add* iryazen war xsen ad ɣarsen sřan. \add Xenni\add* iṭṭef aryaz tayya nnes, issuffeɣ i-tt-dd ɣarsen ɣar barra. Nitni uřyen xas, jeyyḥen tt ǧiřet tekmeř ař tuffut u nitni jjin tt ad tuyur ařami isbeḥ řḥař.
\m 
\v 26 Umi d tarreẓ tuffut, tusa-dd temɣart-a uca tewḍa ɣar tewwart n taddart n weryaz mani \add tuɣa iǧa\add* sidis nnes, \add teqqim din\add* ařami \add i dd-teffeɣ\add* tfawt.
\v 27 \add Umi\add* dd-ikkar sidis ɣar tuffut, yarzem tiwwura n taddart uca iffeɣ ɣar barra, ḥima ad iṭṭef abrid nnes, xzar, din i tewḍa temɣart, tayya nnes, ɣar tewwart n taddart s ifassen nnes x tnebdat.
\v 28 Netta inna as: “Kkar bedd, neccin nexs ad nuyur!” Maca uřa d ijj war xas dd-yarri. \add Xenni\add* issars i-tt x weɣyuř uca iṭṭef abrid ɣar wemcan \add n tzeddiɣt\add* nnes.
\v 29 \add Umi\add* yiweḍ netta ɣar taddart, iksi ijj n řmus, iṭṭef tayya nnes, iqess i-tt x tenɛac n tseqqar uca issekk i-tent ɣar marra jjwayeh n Israil.
\v 30 Uca imsar, aqa qaɛ wenni iẓrin aya, inna: “Man aya ɛemmarṣ ɛad war imsar uřa war t neẓri zeg wass i di ffɣen ayt n Israil zi Miṣra ař ass-a. Xemmem dayes, mcawarem ak-d wayawya uca inim řeḥkam!”
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Amenɣi n ayt n Israil ak-d teqbič n Binyamin
\m 
\v 1 \add Xenni\add* ffɣen marra ayt n Israil, uca tmun tmesmunt am yijj n weryaz ɣar SIDI di Miṣfa, zi Dan ař Bi’r-Sebɛa uřa d tammurt n Jilɛad.
\v 2 Imdebbaren n marra řgens, n marra tiqebbař n Israil, ssbedden ixef nsen di tmesmunt n AREBBI, arebɛa-mya-ařef n yeryazen x iḍaren, \add marra iryazen\add* inni izemmaren x ssif.
\v 3 Ayt n Binyamin sřin, aqa ayt n Israil geɛɛden ɣar Miṣfa. Ayt n Israil nnan: “Siwřem, mammec \add tzemmar\add* ad temsar tuɛeffna-ya?”
\v 4 Aryaz Alawi, aryaz n temɣart ittwanɣen, yarra-dd xasen: “Necc usiɣ-dd ak-d tayya inu zi Jibɛa tenni \add iǧan\add* n Binyamin, ḥima ad ssenseɣ \add din\add*.
\v 5 Uca imezdaɣ n Jibɛa nnqeřben xafi, nnḍen ayi-dd di ǧiřet i taddart, nwan ad ayi nɣen u ɣeṣben tayya inu ařami temmut.
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* ksiɣ tayya inu, bḍiɣ tt d tiseqqar, ssekkeɣ \add ijj n wezyen\add* zzayes ɣar marra jjwayeh n \add temmurt n\add* tesɣart n Israil, minzi nitni ggin řefḍiḥet d tubbuheřya di Israil.
\v 7 Xzar, kenniw marra d ayt n Israil. Arrem-dd kenniw x man aya s wawař d ccwar!”
\m 
\v 8 Uca ibedd řgens imun am yijj n weryaz, inna: “Uřa d ijjen zzayneɣ war iggur ɣar tqiḍunt nnes u uřa d ijjen zzayneɣ war ittɛiqqib ɣar taddart nnes.
\v 9 Ammu i ɣa negg \add xenni řexxu\add* ak-d Jibɛa: ‘\add Ad\add* xas \add neffeɣ\add* ɛlaḥsab taqedduḥt!
\v 10 Ad narecceḥ zi marra tiqebbař n Israil ɛecra n yeryazen zi mya u mya zeg wařef u ařef zi ɛecra-ařaf, ḥima ad awyen řeɛweč i řgens, ḥima, xmi i dd ɣa yasen ɣar Jibɛa tenni \add iǧan\add* n Binyamin, ad zemmaren ad ggen akides ɛlaḥsab marra tubbuheřya nni igga di Israil.”
\m 
\v 11 Munen marra iryazen n Israil di tendint-a, \add tuɣa\add* munen \add ak-d wayawya\add* am yijj n weryaz.
\v 12 Uca sekkent tiqebbař n Israil iryazen ɣar marra taqbič n Binyamin, nnan: “Mana řefḍiḥet-a i ɣarwem imsaren?
\v 13 Xenni řexxu, wcem aneɣ-dd iryazen nni, ayt i war isekkwin i \add iǧan\add* di Jibɛa, ḥima ad ten nenneɣ uca ad ittwamḥa min \add iǧan\add* d aɛeffan zi Israil.” Maca ayt n Binyamin war xsen ad sřen ɣar aytmatsen, ayt n Israil. \f ◼ \fr 20:13 \fk war xsen ad sřen ɣar aytmatsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘war xsen ad sřen ɣar tmijja n aytmatsen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 20:13 \xt Řqḍ. 19:22; Ḥuc. 9:9; 10:9\x*
\m 
\v 14 Usin-dd ayt n Binyamin zi tneddam nsen ɣar Jibɛa munen ḥima ad ffɣen ɣar umenɣi ak-d ayt n Israil.
\v 15 Deg wass nni sedden nitni ayt n Binyamin zi tneddam, setta u-ɛicrin-ařef n yeryazen inni izemmaren i ssif, břa imezdaɣ n Jibɛa i zzaysen ttwafarzen \add ɛad\add* sebɛa-mya n yeryazen.
\v 16 Jar marra řgens-a aqa \add din\add* sebɛa-mya n yeryazen ttwafarzen i war ttwadarrben mliḥ s ufusi nsen afusi. Kuř ijj zzaysen izemmar ad iḥaka mliḥ aṭṭas s yeǧiy \add s ufus uzeřmaḍ\add*, war xeṭṭin. \x ◘ \xo 20:16 \xt Řqḍ. 3:15\x*
\v 17 Uřa d iryazen n Israil ttwasedden. Nhřa ayt n Binyamin tuɣa aten di arebɛa-mya-ařef n yeryazen inni izemmaren x ssif. Marra nitni d iɛeskariyyen.
\m 
\v 18 Kkaren ayt n Israil uca ffɣen ɣar Bayt-Il. Sseqsan AREBBI, nnan: “Man wen zzayneɣ i ɣa iffɣen d amzwaru ɣar umenɣi ak-d ayt n Binyamin?” Inna SIDI: “Amezwaru Yahuda.”
\v 19 Kkaren ayt n Israil ɣar tuffut, wtin iqiḍan nsen ajemmaḍ i Jibɛa
\v 20 Ffɣen yeryazen n Israil ɣar umenɣi ak-d Binyamin uca sedden yeryazen n Israil ixef nsen qibač nsen i umenɣi ɣar Jibɛa.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* ffɣen-dd ayt n Binyamin zi Jibɛa uca ɣeḍřen zi Israil deg wass nni tnayen u-ɛicrin-ařef n yeryazen.
\m 
\v 22 \add Maca\add* řgens, iryazen n Israil, ggin taryast, sedden ixef nsen ict n twařa nneɣnit i umenɣi ɣar mani tuɣa sedden ixef nsen deg wass amezwaru.
\v 23 Uca ayt n Israil geɛɛden, run zzat i wudem n SIDI ař tameddit, sseqsan: “Ma ad ffɣeɣ ict n twařa nneɣnit ɣar umenɣi ak-d iḥenjiren n uma Binyamin?” SIDI yarra-dd: “Gaɛɛdem ḍidd i nnes \add i umenɣi\add*!”
\v 24 Deg wass wiss tnayen qarrben-dd ayt n Israil ɣar ayt n Binyamin,
\v 25 uca iffeɣ Binyamin deg wass wiss tnayen zi Jibɛa maḥend ad kidsen immeřqa. Ɣeḍřen ɛawed tmenṭac-ařef n yeryazen ɣar temmurt, inni tuɣa marra zemmaren x ssif.
\m 
\v 26 \add Xas uca\add* ffɣen marra ayt Israil, řgens marra, uca iwḍen ɣar Bayt-Il, run. Qqimen dinni zzat i wudem n SIDI uca ẓummen deg wass nni ař tameddit uca qeddmen tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣa n řehna zzat i wudem n SIDI.
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* sseqsan ayt n Israil SIDI, minzi \add di Bayt-Il\add* tuɣa din Ttabut n Řɛahd n AREBBI deg wussan nni.
\v 28 Deg wussan nni tuɣa ibedd Finaḥas, mmis n Aliɛazar, mmis n Harun, zzat i wudem nnes uca inna: “Ma ad neffeɣ ict n twařa nneɣnit ɣar umenɣi ak-d arrawen n uma Binyamin niɣ ad \add dayes\add* nesmeḥ?” SIDI yarra-dd: “Ffɣem, maɣar tiwecca ad ten ggeɣ deg ufus nnec.”
\m 
\v 29 \add Xas uca\add* igga Israil řefxux ɣar marra iɣezdisen n Jibɛa. \x ◘ \xo 20:29 \xt Yac. 8:4\x*
\v 30 Deg wass wiss třata geɛɛden ayt n Israil ḍidd i ayt n Binyamin. Sedden ixef nsen \add i umenɣi\add* ak-d Jibɛa, am mammec \add tt ggin\add* twařawin iɛdun.
\v 31 \add Xenni\add* ffɣen ayt n Binyamin i umsagar ak-d ayt n Israil u ttwassiggʷejen x tendint uca, am mammec twařawin iɛdun, bdan ad nɣin \add iryazen\add* zi řgens x ibriden imeqqranen i zzaysen ittgeɛɛed ijj n webrid ɣar Bayt-Il u wenneɣni ɣar Jibɛa, \add nɣin\add* ɛřaḥař třatin n yeryazen n Israil.
\v 32 \add Xenni\add* nnan ayt n Binyamin: “Aqa nitni ttwaɣeřben zzat i wudem nneɣ, am twařa tamezwarut.” \add Xenni\add* nnan ayt n Israil: “Ejj aneɣ ad narweř, ad ten nessiggʷej x tendint ɣar ibriden imeqqranen.”
\v 33 \add Xenni\add* kkaren marra iryazen n Israil zeg wemcan nsen \add innuffaren\add* u sedden ixef nsen \add i umenɣi\add* ɣar Baɛl-Tamar. Di řweqt d ict ffɣen inni zi Israil i tuɣa ggin ijj n řfex zeg wemcan nsen innufaren zeg yefri n Jibɛa.
\v 34 Ɛecra-ařaf n yeryazen ittwafarzen zi marra Israil usin-dd zeg urendad n Jibɛa u amenɣi idweř iwɛar. \add Maca ayt n Binyamin\add* war ssinen, aqa ticti tḥart xasen.
\v 35 SIDI iwta ayt n Binyamin zzat i wudem n Israil, ařami ayt n Israil nɣin deg wass nni xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef u-mya n yeryazen, inni izemmaren marra x ssif.
\v 36 Ẓrin ayt n Binyamin aqa nitni tuɣa ttwawten. \add Xenni\add* wcin iryazen n Israil ttasiɛ i ayt n Binyamin, minzi nitni ttecřen x řfex nni tuɣa ggin ḍidd i Jibɛa.
\v 37 Inni i tuɣa innuffaren, qeǧqen ad ḥejmen x Jibɛa. \add Ammu\add* i ḥejmen inni i tuɣa deg wemcan innuffaren uca wtin marra tandint s řeqḍeɛ n ssif.
\v 38 Iryaz\add en\add* n Israil tuɣa ggin awař ak-d yinni iggin řfex deg wemcan innuffaren, aqa nitni ad jjen aseynu ameqqran n ddexxan ad dd-igeɛɛed zi tendint,
\v 39 \add uca xenni\add* ad nnqeřben iryazen n Israil deg umenɣi. Binyamin tuɣa ibda ad ineɣ inni ittwassnuqqben zi Israil, ɛřaḥař třatin n yeryazen. Aqa nnan: “Nitni ttwawten nican zzat i wudem nneɣ am deg umenɣi amezwaru.”
\v 40 \add DI tsaɛɛet nni\add* ibda useynu ameqqran ad dd-igeɛɛed zi tendint am yijj n uqellij n ddexxan. Umi ixzar Binyamin ɣar ḍeffar, aqa tandint marra tgeɛɛed \add am ddexxan\add* ɣar ujenna.
\v 41 \add Xenni\add* nnqeřben-dd iryazen n Israil uca iryazen n Binyamin iwta i-ten unexřiɛ, minzi nitni ẓrin aqa ticti taɛeffant tuɣa teřqef i-ten.
\v 42 Nitni nnqeřben ɣar řexřa zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil. Amenɣi \add maca\add* iḍfar i-ten, uca inni zi tneddam aqa ggin ict n tɣarṣt tameqqrant di řwesṭ nsen.
\v 43 Nitni nnḍen i ayt n Binyamin, ḍfaren ten břa qeṭṭu, ɛefsen xasen ař amcan n arraḥet qibač n Jibɛa ɣar uɣezdis n \add ccarq\add* manis dd-tneqqar tfuct.
\v 44 Wḍan tmenṭac-ařef n yeryazen, marra nitni d iryazen imeḥḍen.
\v 45 \add Xenni\add* nnqeřben, arewřen ɣar řexřa, ɣar teṣḍart n Rimmun. U x webrid ameqqran qḍan zzaysen x xemsa-ařaf n yeryazen. Ḍfaren ten ař Jidɛum, wtin zzaysen ařfayen n yeryazen \add s řmewt\add*.
\v 46 Deg wass nni tuɣa marra inni iwḍan zi Binyamin di xemsa u-ɛicrin-ařef n yeryazen nni zemmaren x ssif, marra nitni d iryazen imeḥḍen.
\m 
\v 47 Setta-mya n yeryazen \add maca\add* nnqeřben, arewřen ɣar řexřa, ɣar teṣḍart n Rimmun, uca nitni qqimen arebɛa n iyuren di teṣḍart n Rimmun. \x ◘ \xo 20:47 \xt Řqḍ. 21:13\x*
\v 48 Ɛeqben iryazen n Israil ɣar ayt n Binyamin uca wtin ten marra s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, zeg yeryazen n tendint ař řmař d marra min din ufin. Sennej i man aya ssarɣen marra tineddam i ufin deg webrid nsen s tmessi.
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Timɣarin i ayt n Binyamin
\m 
\v 1 Iryaz\add en\add* n Israil tuɣa jjuǧen di Miṣfa uca nnan: “Uřa d ijj zzayneɣ war ittic yeǧis i ayt n Binyamin d tamɣart.”
\v 2 Yusa-dd řgens ɣar Bayt-Il uca qqimen nitni dinni zzat i wudem n AREBBI ař tameddit. Nitni ssgeɛɛden tmijja nsen uca run s imeṭṭawen ittazzřen.
\v 3 Nnan: “\add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, mayemmi imsar uya di Israil, aqa ass-a teqqim ict n teqbič n Israil war tbin?”
\m 
\v 4 Tiwecca nnes, imsar, aqa řgens ikkar zic. Nitni bnan ijj n uɛalṭar, qeddmen xas tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tɣarṣa n řehna.
\v 5 Nnan ayt n Israil: “Wi iqqimen zi marra tiqebbař n Israil war dd-igeɛɛden ɣar wegraw \add n řgens\add* n SIDI?” Tuɣa ggin ict n tjaǧit zi jjihet n wenni war i dd-igeɛɛden ɣar SIDI ɣar Miṣfa, nnan: “Ad ittwaneɣ nican!”
\v 6 Xas uca nedmen ayt n Israil x umatsen Binyamin, nnan: “Ass-a tᵉttwaqess ict n teqbič zi Israil.
\v 7 Mammec i ɣa negg di tmesřact n temɣarin i \add yeryazen n Binyamin\add* nni iqqimen? \add Minzi\add* neccin nejjuǧ ɣar SIDI war d asen nettic ca yessitneɣ d tamɣart.”
\v 8 Nnan: “Ma war dd-igeɛɛed ca n yijjen zi tqebbař n Israil ɣar SIDI di Miṣfa?” Xzar, war dd-yusi uřa d ijjen zi Yabic di Jilɛad ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar, ɣar wegraw \add n řgens\add*,
\v 9 \add minzi\add* řgens ittwaḥseb, u xzar, zi Yabic di Jilɛad war din iǧi uřa d ijjen.
\m 
\v 10 \add Xenni\add* tessekk tmesmunt tenɛac-ařef n yeryazen zeg inni d ayt n umenɣi qaɛ uca umuren ten, nnan: “Gaɛɛdem, wtem imezdaɣ n Yabic di Jilɛad s řeqḍeɛ n ssif, uřa d timɣarin d iḥenjiren imeẓyanen.
\v 11 Ammu i ittxeṣṣa ad teggem: marra min iǧan d awtem d marra timɣarin tinni tuɣa iṭṭṣen ak-d weryaz, ad ten tḥarrmem i uteḥḥi!” \x ◘ \xo 21:11 \xt Řxř. 31:17\x*
\m 
\v 12 Ufin jar imezdaɣ n Yabic di Jilɛad arebɛa-mya n tebřiɣin tinni d tiɛzariyyin, tinni tuɣa ɛad war ṭṭiṣent ak-d weryaz, uca iwyen tent ɣar řmargeḥ n řɛeskar di Cilu di temmurt n Kenɛan.
\v 13 \add Xas uca\add* tessekk tmesmunt tmun \add ireqqasen\add* uca ssiwřen ak-d ayt n Binyamin i \add iǧan\add* ɣar teṣḍart n Rimmun, barrḥen asen s řehna. \x ◘ \xo 21:13 \xt Řqḍ. 20:47\x*
\v 14 Di řweqt nni ɛeqben ayt n Binyamin uca wcin asen timɣarin tinni tuɣa jjin ddarent zi temɣarin n Yabic di Jilɛad. \add Maca\add* tuɣa war ten ttqeddint \add ɛad\add*.
\m 
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* tuɣa řgens izziǧez as Binyamin, maɣar SIDI tuɣa igga tazzit deg iseddiyyen n tqebbař n Israil.
\v 16 Uca imeqqranen n tmesmunt nnan: “Mammec i ɣa negg di tmesřact n temɣarin i \add yeryazen n Binyamin\add* nni iqqimen, minzi timɣarin ttwateḥḥant zi Binyamin.”
\v 17 U nnan ɛawed: “Tasɣart n yinni yarewřen aqa-tt n Binyamin. Ittxeṣṣa war tmeḥḥi uřa d ict n teqbič zi Israil.
\v 18 \add Maca\add* neccin war nzemmar ad asen newc timɣarin zi yessitneɣ, maɣar ayt n Israil jjuǧen, nnan: “Wenni iwcin tamɣart i ayt n Binyamin ad ittwanɛeř.”
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* nnan nitni: “Xzar, zeg useggʷas ař aseggʷas aqa din Řɛid n SIDI di Cilu. Řɛid ittwagg sennej i Bayt-Il, ɣar ccarq n webrid ameqqran i ineddhen zi Bayt-Il ɣar Cakim, ɣar uɣezdis n ljanub n Lebuna.”
\v 20 U nitni ɛeřmen i ayt n Binyamin, nnan: “Uyurem din uca wḍam u ḥḍam deg imarjaɛen n uḍiř.
\v 21 Mařa \add xenni\add* kenniw txezzarem u teẓrim xmi i dd ɣa ffɣent yessis n Cilu, ḥima ad ceḍḥent, ffɣem-dd \add xenni řexdenni\add* zeg imarjaɛen n uḍiř uca ejj ad iṭṭef \add kuř\add* aryaz tamɣart nnes zi yessis n Cilu, u awarni as uyurem ɣar temmurt n Binyamin!
\v 22 Mařa \add xenni\add* babatsent niɣ aytmatsent usin-dd ḥima ad xaneɣ cetcan, ad asen nini: ‘Samḥem aneɣ, jjem ten, minzi deg umenɣi \add ak-d Yabic\add* war nzemmar ad nawi i kuř aryaz tamɣart, u ɛawed kenniw war d asen tent tewcim, niɣ iři řexxu ad daywem yiři d amarwas.’”
\v 23 Uca ammu i ggin ayt n Binyamin. Zi teɛzaryin iceṭṭḥen s nnubtat tinni iṭṭfen, ksin nitni timɣarin ɛlaḥsab řqedd nsen uca ffɣen, ɛeqben ɣar tesɣart nsen uca ssbedden tineddam nsen, ggin zeddɣen daysent.
\m 
\v 24 Di řweqt nni ffɣen-dd ssenni uřa d ayt n Israil, kuř ijj \add yuyur\add* ɣar teqbič nnes u ɣar řaǧ nnes. Ffɣen ssenni, kuř ijjen \add yuyur\add* ɣar tesɣart nnes.
\v 25 Deg wussan nni war tuɣi din ajeǧid di Israil. Kuř ijj ittegg min \add iǧan\add* nican di tiṭṭawin nnes. \x ◘ \xo 21:25 \xt Řqḍ. 17:6; 18:1; 19:1\x* 
